Dialogue: 5,0:01:00.80,0:01:01.65,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:01.65,0:01:02.63,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:10.88,0:01:14.45,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Whatever. I just need to get to the camp on time.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:49.53,0:01:50.63,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Whatcha doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:50.63,0:01:53.03,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Huh? Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:53.79,0:01:54.92,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,I'm lost.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:56.59,0:01:58.64,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,What? Are you from another town?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:00.45,0:02:01.10,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:08.02,0:02:09.57,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Is that fun?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:09.57,0:02:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:11.78,0:02:13.03,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:13.38,0:02:15.42,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,This is just a time waster.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:16.99,0:02:17.93,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:19.09,0:02:20.37,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Do you play volleyball?!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:20.37,0:02:20.95,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:21.70,0:02:22.96,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Those shoes!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:23.51,0:02:24.63,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,They're volleyball shoes!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:24.63,0:02:26.42,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:26.77,0:02:28.40,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,I play volleyball too!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:28.40,0:02:30.38,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,My name's Hinata Shouyou!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:31.31,0:02:32.31,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Kozume...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:33.27,0:02:34.09,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Kenma.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:36.54,0:02:38.95,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Um, do you like volleyball?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:40.28,0:02:41.64,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:41.64,0:02:43.31,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,I play it 'cause it's there.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:43.84,0:02:47.71,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,I don't mind it, I guess, but I don't like getting tired out.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:48.48,0:02:53.98,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,But a friend of mine plays it, \Nand he probably needs me to play with him.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:56.10,0:02:59.33,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,I think once you start to like it, you'll find it's way more fun.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:59.33,0:03:00.39,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:00.39,0:03:03.02,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,I'm only doing it for the duration of high school.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:25.38,0:03:28.10,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Kenma, wake up!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:32.07,0:03:34.09,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Everyone's gone for breakfast already.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:34.09,0:03:35.66,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Get a move on, man.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:40.13,0:03:41.87,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Get up, damn it!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:47.12,0:03:51.22,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Morning! It's finally time! Isn't that super exciting?!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:51.22,0:03:52.99,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Get a text from Shorty?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.24,0:03:59.95,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Kinda funny he'll just text someone he's about to face off with.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:00.90,0:04:04.23,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,He's gonna come at you with all he's got.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:06.56,0:04:10.05,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,I mean, isn't it natural to want to win?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:10.78,0:04:13.90,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,No, I mean that he's gonna go all-out on {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:16.17,0:04:17.75,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
