Dialogue: 5,0:05:10.17,0:05:13.96,Default,Naoi,0,0,0,,It's finally time for the Battle of the Garbage Dumpster, Coach Nekomata!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:14.24,0:05:15.75,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:15.75,0:05:21.18,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,But we didn't come here just to beat Karasuno.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:21.78,0:05:28.52,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,There are quite a few people with a bit of an interest in this match.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.27,0:05:28.52,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1434,518)\fscx28\fscy28\frz-0.59\fax-0.11\fnCrayon Hand Regular 2016 Demo\c&HCDCDCB&\blur1.1}Starting at 10 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.27,0:05:28.52,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1422,575)\fscx28\fscy28\frz-0.59\fax-0.11\fnCrayon Hand Regular 2016 Demo\c&HCDCDCB&\blur1.1}Volleyball Nationals
