Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.27,0:05:28.52,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1423,724)\fscx20\fscy20\frz359\fax-0.1\fnCrayon Hand Regular 2016 Demo\c&HB8BCB2&\blur1.1}Holding a small watch party
