Dialogue: 5,0:05:29.70,0:05:31.68,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,Including me, of course.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:31.68,0:05:32.65,Default,Daichi,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:32.65,0:05:34.68,Default,All,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:35.30,0:05:39.74,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,These kids don't aren't here for our old rivalry.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.54,0:05:41.89,Default,Keishin,0,0,0,,Coach Nekomata.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:43.78,0:05:44.92,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:44.92,0:05:47.08,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,May the best team win.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:48.11,0:05:50.50,Default,Takeda,0,0,0,,We've brought our all today!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:52.72,0:05:54.19,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,We accept your challenge.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:56.64,0:06:01.22,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Well, well, well, if it isn't Karasuno, the diving drill pros.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.01,0:06:07.37,Default,Daichi,0,0,0,,We do our best.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:09.61,0:06:11.73,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,We're here watching matches two days in a row.
