Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.12,0:06:15.15,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,I'm starting to think you're secretly rooting for Nekoma.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.52,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,N-N-No way!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:17.52,0:06:20.79,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,I just wanna be here when they lose!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.79,0:06:23.40,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,Come on, just admit it.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:23.40,0:06:26.03,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,N-No, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:28.03,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(304,347)\fscx66\fscy66\frz17.62\fax-0.1\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&HE2E2E2&\blur1.1}T{\frz17.516\fax-0.098}o{\frz17.413\fax-0.097}k{\frz17.309\fax-0.095}y{\frz17.205\fax-0.094}o {\frz16.998\fax-0.091}M{\frz16.895\fax-0.089}u{\frz16.791\fax-0.088}n{\frz16.687\fax-0.086}i{\frz16.584\fax-0.085}c{\frz16.48\fax-0.083}i{\frz16.376\fax-0.082}p{\frz16.273\fax-0.08}a{\frz16.169\fax-0.079}l {\frz15.962\fax-0.076}N{\frz15.858\fax-0.074}e{\frz15.755\fax-0.073}k{\frz15.651\fax-0.071}o{\frz15.547\fax-0.07}m{\frz15.444\fax-0.068}a {\frz15.236\fax-0.065}H{\frz15.133\fax-0.064}i{\frz15.029\fax-0.062}g{\frz14.925\fax-0.061}h {\frz14.718\fax-0.058}S{\frz14.615\fax-0.056}c{\frz14.511\fax-0.055}h{\frz14.407\fax-0.053}o{\frz14.304\fax-0.052}o{\frz14.2\fax-0.05}l
Dialogue: 5,0:06:28.31,0:06:30.26,Default,Karasuno and Nekoma,0,0,0,,Let's have a good match!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:31.00,0:06:33.75,Default,Saeko,0,0,0,,Lemme hear you!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:34.25,0:06:37.46,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,We absolutely cannot let them out-cheer us!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.29,0:06:41.24,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,Go, go, Nekoma!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:42.76,0:06:44.44,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,Push it, push it, Nekoma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:45.76,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1460,940)\fscx80\fscy87\fnLeviBrush\c&HD6D3D3&\alpha&HE0&\blur7.5}Fly
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.76,0:06:45.76,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1460,940)\fscx80\fscy87\fnLeviBrush\c&HD6D3D3&\blur1}Fly
Dialogue: 5,0:06:45.76,0:06:47.85,Default,Nekoma Cheering Squad,0,0,0,,Go, go, Nekoma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:48.76,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(722,789)\fscx42\fscy42\frz4.1\fax-0.08\fnDIST Inking Bold\fsp4.5\b1\c&H19131F&\blur1.3}Connect
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.11,0:06:53.49,Default,Bokuto,0,0,0,,No fair! I wanna play Karasuno and Nekoma!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:53.49,0:06:54.48,Default,Akaashi,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:54.48,0:06:57.94,Default,Nekoma Cheering Squad,0,0,0,,Yamamoto, go get 'em!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:58.51,0:07:00.74,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Yeah! You just wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:00.74,0:07:03.76,Default,Azumane,0,0,0,,The Tokyo teams have plenty of people cheering for them.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.76,0:07:05.66,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Stinkin' locals.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:06.10,0:07:07.51,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,All right, Kenma!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:07.51,0:07:10.07,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Let's stop the monster and his team!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:10.07,0:07:13.65,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,Our blockers getting split up would be a real pain.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.52,0:07:18.52,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kenma's not very interested in winning or losing.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:18.52,0:07:21.38,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Words like that won't change that.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:21.81,0:07:25.59,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,{\i1}He just analyzes if something is possible or not.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.54,0:07:28.18,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can we do this or not?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:29.99,0:07:31.56,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:35.62,0:07:37.23,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,All right! You know the deal!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:46.72,0:07:48.82,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,We're like the blood in our veins.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:49.16,0:07:51.03,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,We must flow without stopping.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:51.03,0:07:52.99,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Keep the oxygen pumping...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:53.36,0:07:56.96,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,and your minds working!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:57.28,0:08:00.00,Default,Kuroo and Sawamura,0,0,0,,Let's tear these guys up!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.25,Default,Nekoma and Karasuno,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:03.55,0:08:06.84,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,We will now introduce both teams' starting lineups.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:07.44,0:08:12.30,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,First up, we have Karasuno High School, who defeated the tournament favorite Inarizaki the other day.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:12.92,0:08:17.73,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,Wearing number one, captain and support pillar of Karasuno, the wing spiker Sawamura Daichi.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:15.97,0:08:17.23,Default,Daichi,0,0,0,,{\an8}I want to hear you!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:17.23,0:08:17.73,Default,Karasuno,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:17.73,0:08:19.23,Default,Azumane,0,0,0,,{\an8}R-Right.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:18.11,0:08:23.23,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,Wearing number three, wing spiker and Karasuno's main offensive power and ace, Azumane Asahi.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:23.72,0:08:26.61,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,Wearing number five, the up-and-coming secret ace,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:26.61,0:08:30.20,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,second-year wing spiker Tanaka Ryuunosuke.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:30.50,0:08:35.66,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,Wearing number nine, first-year setter Kageyama Tobio, \Nwho's suddenly in the spotlight.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:36.16,0:08:38.18,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,Wearing number ten, another guy in the spotlight,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:38.18,0:08:41.63,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,a middle blocker and the smallest player in the tournament, Hinata Shouyou.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.14,0:08:47.84,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,Weaning number eleven, the tallest on the team and their key defender, middle blocker Tsukishima Kei.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:48.83,0:08:52.80,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,Wearing number four is their libero, Nishinoya Yuu. He's the team's guardian angel and spark plug.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:53.26,0:08:55.77,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,They'll be led by Head Coach Takeda Ittetsu.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:56.27,0:09:00.01,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,And since he doesn't have volleyball experience,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:00.01,0:09:03.65,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,Coach Ukai Keishin will be giving out the actual directions.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:06.52,0:09:07.74,Default,Ukai,0,0,0,,That's my grandson.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:08.12,0:09:10.31,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,What? That's amazing!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:10.31,0:09:11.95,Default,Patient 1,0,0,0,,He's so young!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:15.66,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(412,277)\fscx42\fscy42\fnIwata Mincho Old Pro-Fate B\c&H433736&\blur1.1}Mr. Ukai Ikkei
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:15.66,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(412,390)\fscx42\fscy42\fnIwata Mincho Old Pro-Fate B\c&H433736&\blur1.1}Mr. Morimori Morio
Dialogue: 5,0:09:12.63,0:09:14.38,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,He looks just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:18.16,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1055,728)\fscx64\fscy64\fnDIST Inking Bold\fsp4.5\b1\c&H211B29&\blur1.3}Connect
Dialogue: 5,0:09:16.52,0:09:18.16,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,Next up, we have Nekoma High School.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:19.03,0:09:23.83,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,Wearing number one and captain, Kuroo Tetsuro, \Nan all-rounder playing middle blocker.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:24.24,0:09:30.80,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,Wearing number two, the well-rounded and cool-headed third-year wing spiker, Kai Nobuyuki.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:31.30,0:09:35.76,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,Wearing number four, the second-year ace, Yamamoto Taketora. He's their main scorer.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:36.45,0:09:37.99,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\an8}Shut up, Tora.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:36.45,0:09:40.54,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,Wearing number five, the brains of Nekoma and their setter, Kozume Kenma.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:40.54,0:09:43.48,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,We've all seen that there's more to him than meets the eye.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:43.96,0:09:50.49,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,Wearing number six, with hard-to-read attacks, second-year wing spiker Fukunaga Shouhei.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:51.11,0:09:55.31,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,Wearing number eleven, \Nhis height and wits see him becoming a star player,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.31,0:09:58.41,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,it's first-year middle blocker Haiba Lev.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.31,0:09:57.75,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,{\an8}Give me all the sets, please!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:59.00,0:10:00.69,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,{\an8}How stupid are you?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:59.00,0:10:03.54,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,Playing libero and wearing number three, Nekoma's ace defender, Yaku Morisuke.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:03.92,0:10:06.34,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,They're being led by Coach Nekomata Yasufumi.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:06.34,0:10:07.34,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:07.34,0:10:09.83,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,This guy's your rival, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:09.83,0:10:11.34,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,Coach Nekomonster!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:11.34,0:10:13.56,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,It's Coach Nekomata!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:13.56,0:10:16.59,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,Didn't you want to be at this match?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:17.60,0:10:20.31,Default,Ukai,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:20.99,0:10:27.09,Default,Ukai,0,0,0,,My name might not be in the tournament pamphlet, \Nbut my student is there.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:27.92,0:10:30.53,Default,Ukai,0,0,0,,And my own flesh and blood.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:31.56,0:10:33.36,Default,Ukai,0,0,0,,What else do I need?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:34.61,0:10:37.03,Default,Keishin,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is about here and now.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:37.03,0:10:38.72,Default,Keishin,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's their battle.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:39.37,0:10:43.19,Default,Keishin,0,0,0,,{\i1}But we wouldn't have made it here on our own.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.90,0:10:46.83,Default,Keishin,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure those guys know that.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:47.53,0:10:50.57,Default,Keishin,0,0,0,,{\i1}So sit back and enjoy, gramps!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:00.68,0:11:02.11,Default,Akiteru,0,0,0,,He got it up on the first serve!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:01.18,0:11:03.05,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nice receive!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:08.69,0:11:10.11,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,Someone get that!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:15.74,0:11:16.95,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,{\i1}That packed a punch!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:16.95,0:11:18.41,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,We can score here!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:19.74,0:11:21.20,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Send it left!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:23.14,0:11:25.00,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}Watch this spike!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:26.89,0:11:28.71,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,Nice one, Taketora!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:29.05,0:11:30.17,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the air too long...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:33.61,0:11:34.96,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,Nice, Daichi!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:46.00,0:11:47.48,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Lately, I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:48.08,0:11:49.22,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Thinking what?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:49.22,0:11:55.43,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,You're fun to play against, \Nso I'd like to face you in a real match.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:56.05,0:11:56.79,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:58.47,0:12:02.08,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,A match where losing means an instant game over.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:05.60,0:12:06.41,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:14.74,0:12:16.01,Default,Takinoue,0,0,0,,Holy crap!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:17.92,0:12:19.59,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,That was so fast!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:24.69,0:12:27.89,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,This is our match where there's no extra lives, Kenma!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:32.96,0:12:37.95,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,It's on now!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:44.10,0:12:47.10,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Shouyou's changed since we came to nationals.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:47.10,0:12:51.45,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,We can't assume he'll always come jumping first.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:54.60,0:12:56.57,Default,Karasuno,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:57.54,0:13:00.29,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,He still does come up fast sometimes, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:00.29,0:13:01.76,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Sure does.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:02.12,0:13:07.70,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Shorty's trying to lure us out with those minus tempo attacks.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:09.06,0:13:12.37,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,When did we last practice with them? October?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:12.37,0:13:15.07,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,They've already changed things up?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:15.07,0:13:17.55,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Ugh, gimme a break.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:18.38,0:13:19.88,Default,Fukunaga,0,0,0,,But the cat caught the snake.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:20.82,0:13:22.07,Default,Fukunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cat{\i0}ch and releasssse.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:25.17,0:13:28.08,Default,Kai,0,0,0,,Right. They're not the only ones who've improved.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:31.62,0:13:33.71,Default,Kuroo; Fukunaga; Yamamoto; Kai,0,0,0,,Synchronized attack!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:38.16,0:13:38.80,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,I touched it!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:38.80,0:13:40.26,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Nice call!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:40.60,0:13:41.49,Default,Sawamura,0,0,0,,Get it!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:43.11,0:13:44.72,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{\i1}A synchronized attack...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:45.06,0:13:45.99,Default,Hinata; Sawamura; Tsukishima; Tanaka; Azumane,0,0,0,,{\i1}...with the whole team!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:47.15,0:13:49.02,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,{\i1}Five attackers?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:55.61,0:13:59.07,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,Nice one, nice one, Kuroo!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.53,Default,Sawamura,0,0,0,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:03.67,0:14:06.24,Default,Chigaya,0,0,0,,Nekoma also did a synchronized attack, didn't they?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:04.96,0:14:06.24,Default,Azumane,0,0,0,,{\an8}Come on! Focus!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:06.52,0:14:09.67,Default,Ogano,0,0,0,,Looks like the cats and crows are both omnivores.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:09.67,0:14:11.62,Default,Gora,0,0,0,,Real cats are carnivores.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:12.56,0:14:13.58,Default,Ogano,0,0,0,,Thanks for the info.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:14.12,0:14:17.29,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,That's the first time we've used the five-man attack on them, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:17.29,0:14:20.20,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,Didn't slow Kuroo down one bit.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:20.20,0:14:25.89,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Remember, Kuroo taught Tsukishima how to do those annoyingly persistent blocks.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:25.89,0:14:30.22,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,The ball's getting by you because your still have your hands up.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:30.56,0:14:35.09,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you that you gotta reach forward, Mr. Clubb?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:35.09,0:14:38.69,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,Must be feeling confident if you're dishing out advice.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.69,0:14:41.61,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Nope. Just egging you on.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:42.99,0:14:46.76,Default,Bokuto,0,0,0,,Don't let him beat you, Tsukki! Get him back for that!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:44.60,0:14:49.12,Default,Akaashi,0,0,0,,{\an8}I bet Kuroo's saying something to piss off Tsukishima again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:51.08,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(488,204)\fscx59\fscy97\frz-2.02\fax0.05\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Nekoma
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:51.08,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1217,236)\fscx76\fscy125\frz-2.02\fax0.05\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Karasuno
Dialogue: 5,0:14:51.47,0:14:53.04,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,Make it good!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:54.64,0:14:55.71,Default,Sawamura,0,0,0,,Move up!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:57.37,0:14:58.33,Default,Sawamura,0,0,0,,Left!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:04.68,0:15:06.43,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,You call that a receive?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.84,0:15:08.14,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,It's gonna go over the net.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:07.41,0:15:09.05,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,{\an8}Send it back, Hinata!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:12.02,0:15:12.89,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:17.86,0:15:20.07,Default,Nishinoya and Azumane,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:20.07,0:15:22.21,Default,Alisa,0,0,0,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:23.77,0:15:27.00,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,Yuu! You're better every time we play!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:27.00,0:15:29.16,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,Thanks, Morisuke!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:29.60,0:15:33.87,Default,Ogano,0,0,0,,Not too long ago, he couldn't time it right at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:34.45,0:15:39.94,Default,Naoi,0,0,0,,This goes without saying, but they play like a completely different team than last time.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:39.94,0:15:42.13,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,Scary, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:42.56,0:15:45.05,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,Like true omnivores.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:45.98,0:15:49.80,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,They've taken down beasts bigger than them.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:51.64,0:15:53.52,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:53.85,0:15:55.14,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,How do we beat 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:59.44,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(382,243)\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Nekoma
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:59.44,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1522,243)\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Karasuno
Dialogue: 5,0:15:59.80,0:16:01.15,Default,Yachi,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:02.33,0:16:03.37,Default,Yachi,0,0,0,,Here's their chance!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:03.86,0:16:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming back!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:06.28,0:16:07.11,Default,Yachi,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:07.49,0:16:08.50,Default,Alisa,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:08.50,0:16:10.07,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,Keep it going!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:10.36,0:16:11.26,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:11.26,0:16:14.79,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,{\i1}These guys have never played the same twice.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:15.08,0:16:16.75,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,{\i1}So just like always,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:16.75,0:16:20.29,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,{\i1}we gotta watch, adjust, and figure 'em out!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:21.25,0:16:22.63,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Left, left!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:25.59,0:16:27.04,Default,Karasuno,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:27.04,0:16:29.80,Default,Azumane,0,0,0,,{\i1}How many times am I gonna jump today?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:30.64,0:16:33.76,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,You show 'em, Tsukishima! Don't let Kuroo beat you!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:33.76,0:16:37.49,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,{\an8}You hear me?! Don't you dare lose to him!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:34.24,0:16:37.06,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Suga is as heated as ever.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:37.06,0:16:39.98,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,He gets way more fired up than you'd think, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:37.49,0:16:39.98,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,{\an8}Are you listening, Tsukishima?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:40.49,0:16:41.90,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,That's not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:44.88,0:16:46.15,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Back already.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:47.59,0:16:52.20,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,I'd never dream of beating someone who's better than me.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:52.49,0:16:54.46,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,Me beat you?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:54.46,0:16:56.71,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,No way! Never!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:56.71,0:17:00.12,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,I never thought for a second that I could win on my own.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:01.31,0:17:04.84,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,A certain someone seems to think he might.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:05.28,0:17:06.58,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.31,0:17:10.16,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,He {\i1}is{\i0} always one step ahead of me.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:13.81,0:17:15.57,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,You got this, Yamaguchi!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:16.10,0:17:17.64,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,{\i1}C'mon, c'mon, c'mon!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:16.10,0:17:18.06,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,{\an8}Bring it!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:20.59,0:17:21.65,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:25.52,0:17:27.44,Default,Yamaguchi,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:27.44,0:17:30.40,Default,Akiteru,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes! Yes, yes, yes!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:30.40,0:17:32.39,Default,Alisa,0,0,0,,The ball went all flop mid-air!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:33.64,0:17:35.37,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,That was a nice serve!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:36.97,0:17:39.49,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,Shifted just at your fingertips, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:39.49,0:17:40.33,Default,Kai,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:40.33,0:17:42.90,Default,Alisa,0,0,0,,Tadashi... He's all grown up...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:42.90,0:17:44.00,Default,Shimada,0,0,0,,Sure is!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:44.00,0:17:44.98,Default,Takinoue,0,0,0,,You his dad?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:45.86,0:17:48.14,Default,Reserves,0,0,0,,Go for one more!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:48.14,0:17:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Get 'em!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:53.22,0:17:55.61,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nekoma doesn't give "one more"!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:58.48,0:17:59.60,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,Nice receive!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:03.06,0:18:04.27,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,{\i1}All we needed.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:08.47,0:18:11.40,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Didn't I tell you that you gotta reach forward, Mr. Clubb?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:16.53,0:18:19.24,Default,Karasuno,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:22.76,0:18:25.06,Default,Bokuto,0,0,0,,That's what our Tsukki is made of!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:25.06,0:18:27.67,Default,Akaashi,0,0,0,,Tsukishima's not on our team, Bokuto.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:34.93,0:18:36.14,Default,Yamaguchi,0,0,0,,Nice block!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:36.50,0:18:37.48,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,Nice serve.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:38.51,0:18:39.83,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,That's on you!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:39.83,0:18:41.06,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:41.06,0:18:44.06,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,How was that on me?! Tsukki just played it right!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:44.34,0:18:46.73,Default,Fukunaga,0,0,0,,That jump was so high...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:46.73,0:18:48.58,Default,Fukunaga,0,0,0,,Maybe the crows can fly.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:51.29,0:18:54.49,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Tsukki, how're you enjoying this these days?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:59.11,0:19:00.33,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,Thankfully,
Dialogue: 5,0:19:01.96,0:19:04.59,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,it's fun, every now and then.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:06.60,0:19:09.55,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Never thought I'd see the day you'd say so!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:09.55,0:19:11.77,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,You could learn a thing or two, Kenma!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.07,0:19:16.37,Default,Reserves,0,0,0,,Give us another good one, Yamaguchi!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.97,0:19:20.85,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Nice receive!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:20.40,0:19:20.85,Default,Sawamura,0,0,0,,{\an8}Right!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:23.10,0:19:25.17,Default,Nekoma,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:26.06,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(382,243)\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Nekoma
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:26.06,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1522,243)\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Karasuno
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.07,0:19:29.27,Default,Yamaguchi,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:29.88,0:19:31.81,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,You should feel good about that.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:31.81,0:19:36.36,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Guess I woulda wanted to score more too, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:36.80,0:19:40.01,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,All right! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:42.22,0:19:44.09,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,Yamamoto! Make it count!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:46.12,0:19:46.46,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:47.37,0:19:48.23,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,Now's our chance!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:51.80,0:19:52.80,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's long!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:52.80,0:19:53.92,Default,Sawamura,0,0,0,,Asahi!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:56.30,0:19:57.78,Default,Keshin,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:57.78,0:20:00.76,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,Keep your hands on the ball and you'll get your chance.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:00.76,0:20:03.63,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,We don't need a perfect pass if you're just getting it over the net!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:03.63,0:20:04.79,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:04.79,0:20:07.31,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,It's not a perfect pass if it goes over the net anyway.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:07.31,0:20:08.35,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:08.35,0:20:10.46,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,All right already!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:10.46,0:20:12.57,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,Kageyama's something, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:13.43,0:20:15.15,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,You don't need to get it to the net.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:15.15,0:20:18.41,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,Get it up to the attack line and I'll handle the rest.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:18.93,0:20:21.37,Default,Tanaka; Azumane; Nishinoya; Sawamura; Hinata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn him for being so cool!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:21.92,0:20:23.46,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,You hear that, Kenma?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:23.46,0:20:25.72,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Man, that guy says some cool things.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:25.72,0:20:26.81,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,I heard him.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:27.50,0:20:30.62,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,We have our rules, they have theirs.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:30.62,0:20:32.09,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Okay, {\i1}Mom{\i0}.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:32.09,0:20:35.21,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,We don't need to compete every step of the way.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:33.80,0:20:35.21,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hinata, you got this!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:36.55,0:20:37.79,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,Fukunaga!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:37.79,0:20:38.88,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Center!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:40.22,0:20:40.76,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:40.76,0:20:41.43,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:44.39,0:20:45.85,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,{\i1}The other side?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:47.81,0:20:49.84,Default,Saeko,0,0,0,,Nice spike!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:50.86,0:20:52.47,Default,Saeko,0,0,0,,What?! No way!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.35,0:20:56.49,Default,Saeko,0,0,0,,All right! That was close!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.36,0:20:55.87,Default,Karasuno,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:57.48,0:20:58.99,Default,Nekoma Girl,0,0,0,,So close!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:58.99,0:21:02.61,Default,Sawamura,0,0,0,,We thought it was a done deal, \Nbut they didn't think it was over yet.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:03.30,0:21:05.77,Default,Sawamura and Tanaka,0,0,0,,Nekoma always plays like that, so stay alert!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:08.50,0:21:15.04,Default,Shimada,0,0,0,,Kageyama was going hard right, but he set that perfectly to the left.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:15.04,0:21:16.16,Default,Takinoue,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:16.16,0:21:20.30,Default,Takinoue,0,0,0,,And the guys on offense were fully ready for it.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:21.07,0:21:23.13,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Nice stuff.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:23.13,0:21:26.38,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Intrigue and respect rather than fear.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:26.38,0:21:30.56,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,{\i1}The joy of facing off against a tough opponent held in high regard.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:31.61,0:21:33.40,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,You gotta love it.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:34.44,0:21:37.62,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he's a little different.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:38.03,0:21:42.07,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the big event. A long-awaited clash.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:39.35,0:21:41.06,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,{\an8}Bring it!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:42.07,0:21:45.24,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could be the last match for the third-years.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:45.83,0:21:49.75,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he's not interested in all that.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:49.75,0:21:55.24,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,{\i1}All he wants to do is pluck the feathers from those crows.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:59.78,0:22:01.01,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,Asahi!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:05.03,0:22:08.43,Default,Ogano,0,0,0,,Karasuno's offense is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:08.72,0:22:11.63,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,They're actually doing pretty well, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:11.63,0:22:13.84,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,Who is? Nekoma?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:13.84,0:22:14.90,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.90,0:22:17.11,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(382,243)\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Nekoma
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.90,0:22:17.11,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1522,243)\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Karasuno
Dialogue: 5,0:22:15.25,0:22:16.55,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,Even though they aren't winning?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:17.11,0:22:21.11,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,Nekoma are down early a lot of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.99,0:22:21.11,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(779,238)\fscx82\fscy82\frz340.2\fax0.36\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H1E2123&\alpha&HD0&\blur7.5}Nekoma
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.99,0:22:21.11,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(779,238)\fscx82\fscy82\frz340.2\fax0.36\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H1E2123&\blur1.2}Nekoma
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.99,0:22:21.11,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1559,528)\fscx59\fscy59\frz340.2\fax0.36\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H1E2123&\alpha&HD0&\blur7.5}Nohebi
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.99,0:22:21.11,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1559,528)\fscx59\fscy59\frz340.2\fax0.36\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H1E2123&\blur1.2}Nohebi
Dialogue: 5,0:22:21.11,0:22:25.52,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,But they spend that time learning their opponent's moves.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:25.52,0:22:29.70,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,Nekoma's style is to come clawing back.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:29.70,0:22:32.84,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,They're up against some heavy-hitters today, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:32.84,0:22:36.54,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,And they're still hanging on this close from the start.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:36.54,0:22:40.62,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,This is a pretty amazing show from them.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:40.62,0:22:41.42,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,Daichi!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:41.78,0:22:42.44,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,Too much air!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:42.44,0:22:43.88,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Give it to 'em, Kageyama!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:43.88,0:22:45.93,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,Hold your ground, Lev!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:46.80,0:22:48.49,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,{\i1}You got this, Lev!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:48.49,0:22:50.35,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can't outplay him...
Dialogue: 5,0:22:50.35,0:22:52.03,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Definitely can't!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:52.03,0:22:53.85,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,{\i1}But you've got height on him!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:55.96,0:22:56.94,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Figures.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:58.36,0:22:59.34,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Kenma!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:00.34,0:23:01.32,Default,Hinata; Nekomata; Inuoka; Yaku; Akaashi; Bokuto,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:01.32,0:23:03.03,Default,Hinata; Nekomata; Inuoka; Yaku; Akaashi; Bokuto,0,0,0,,He can move!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:06.34,0:23:08.24,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:08.24,0:23:10.52,Default,Alisa,0,0,0,,Levochka!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:10.52,0:23:11.45,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,That height!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:11.45,0:23:13.17,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,That was a little low!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:13.17,0:23:14.42,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:14.42,0:23:15.67,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,Kozume...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:17.47,0:23:18.81,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,You can actually move.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:20.72,0:23:23.63,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,I mean... I am alive.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:24.22,0:23:26.93,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Kageyama doesn't have you beat at all!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:27.32,0:23:28.89,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Do you hear yourself?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:29.25,0:23:30.92,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Huh? Was that bad?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:30.92,0:23:34.52,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,It's rude to compare me to someone who's clearly working hard.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:35.50,0:23:38.77,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,But when I see something that amazing...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:39.61,0:23:44.16,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,I can't help but feel like maybe I can do more too.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:48.08,0:23:50.22,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,Shoulda figured, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:50.22,0:23:53.17,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,They're not the same as before either.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.62,0:23:58.58,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(328,236)\fscx90\fscy70\fax-0.17\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}N{\fax-0.156}e{\fax-0.142}k{\fax-0.128}o{\fax-0.114}m{\fax-0.1}a
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.62,0:23:58.58,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1598,237)\fscx90\fscy70\fax0.08\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}K{\fax0.087}a{\fax0.094}r{\fax0.101}a{\fax0.109}s{\fax0.116}u{\fax0.123}n{\fax0.13}o
Dialogue: 5,0:24:00.48,0:24:01.61,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Make it count!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:02.48,0:24:03.34,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:05.64,0:24:06.57,Default,Azumane,0,0,0,,Nice receive!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:06.57,0:24:09.14,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like that wasn't an easy serve!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:09.41,0:24:11.45,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,{\an8}Left!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:09.90,0:24:12.60,Default,Yachi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hinata's not an easy target when it comes to receives anymore!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:14.84,0:24:17.27,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right through three blockers!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:17.55,0:24:20.72,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,Don't you dare get cocky just from bumping the damn ball!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:21.23,0:24:23.50,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,I-I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.25,0:24:40.46,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(382,243)\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Nekoma
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.25,0:24:40.46,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1522,243)\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Karasuno
Dialogue: 5,0:24:39.06,0:24:40.46,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Center!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:41.91,0:24:42.92,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,I touched it!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:43.83,0:24:44.47,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Fukunaga!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:44.47,0:24:45.88,Default,Sawamura,0,0,0,,To the left!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:46.21,0:24:47.26,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,Kageyama!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:47.26,0:24:48.12,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,Sorry! Back me up!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:48.12,0:24:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Asahi!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:48.58,0:24:52.03,Default,Ogano,0,0,0,,Whoa now, we're only in the first set!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:52.03,0:24:53.85,Default,Gora,0,0,0,,That's rough.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:58.77,0:25:00.44,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,Sorry! That was wide!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:59.49,0:25:00.44,Default,Yachi,0,0,0,,{\an8}He's gonna lose an arm!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:00.44,0:25:01.90,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,All yours, Kenma!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:11.47,0:25:13.03,Default,Karasuno,0,0,0,,{\an8}All right!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:12.51,0:25:14.14,Default,Saeko,0,0,0,,Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:14.14,0:25:14.93,Default,Shimada,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:14.93,0:25:15.74,Default,Saeko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:25:17.26,0:25:18.50,Default,Azumane,0,0,0,,A reaching foul?
Dialogue: 5,0:25:19.74,0:25:24.19,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,{\i1}He made it look like a dump to draw the foul?
Dialogue: 5,0:25:25.79,0:25:27.73,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}I might actually be good at this.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:29.07,0:25:31.14,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,Just one more point!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.92,0:25:32.39,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(796,253)\fscx92\fscy92\frz340.2\fax0.36\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Nekoma
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.92,0:25:32.39,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1579,547)\fscx49\fscy49\frz340.2\fax0.36\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Karasuno
Dialogue: 5,0:25:35.23,0:25:36.52,Default,Yamaguchi,0,0,0,,Nice receive!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:36.52,0:25:37.68,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:38.00,0:25:39.89,Default,Azumane; Tanaka; Sawamura; Tsukishima,0,0,0,,{\i1}Synchronized attack!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:40.36,0:25:41.98,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,Not this again.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:46.27,0:25:47.05,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:47.69,0:25:48.85,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:48.85,0:25:50.15,Default,Reserves,0,0,0,,Here's our chance!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:53.62,0:25:56.66,Default,Akaashi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Karasuno's consistently attacking with their whole team.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:56.66,0:25:59.58,Default,Bokuto,0,0,0,,They sure are making Nekoma's defense move.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:03.77,0:26:04.58,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Get it over!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:06.90,0:26:08.55,Default,Takinouke,0,0,0,,He'll be lucky to even get that over!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:08.55,0:26:10.47,Default,Yamaguchi; Hinata; Sugawara,0,0,0,,Go again!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:14.68,0:26:16.39,Default,Karasuno,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here it comes!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:16.70,0:26:18.10,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,{\i1}One more go!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:18.72,0:26:19.81,Default,Tsukishima and Tanaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}Room to run...
Dialogue: 5,0:26:20.39,0:26:21.52,Default,Sawamura,0,0,0,,{\i1}Secured!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:37.73,0:26:40.26,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,I can hardly believe my eyes!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:40.26,0:26:42.87,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,The entire Karasuno team misread that play!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:42.87,0:26:45.45,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,This will cost Karasuno the first set.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.87,0:26:48.71,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348,239)\fscx90\fscy70\fax-0.17\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}N{\fax-0.156}e{\fax-0.142}k{\fax-0.128}o{\fax-0.114}m{\fax-0.1}a
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.87,0:26:48.71,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1607,240)\fscx90\fscy70\fax0.08\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}K{\fax0.087}a{\fax0.094}r{\fax0.101}a{\fax0.109}s{\fax0.116}u{\fax0.123}n{\fax0.13}o
Dialogue: 5,0:26:45.45,0:26:48.13,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,Which means Nekoma takes the lead!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:49.01,0:26:52.31,Default,Habuka,0,0,0,,Well, that misread was a part of it, sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:52.31,0:26:53.30,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:26:53.85,0:26:56.08,Default,Habuka,0,0,0,,On Kozume's return there,
Dialogue: 5,0:26:56.08,0:27:01.81,Default,Habuka,0,0,0,,he saw the spikers all moving in for the attack and aimed just between them.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:02.45,0:27:06.27,Default,Habuka,0,0,0,,It was also right along the path that Kageyama took to be ready for the set.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:06.80,0:27:11.72,Default,Habuka,0,0,0,,Right where their positions cross, and opposite the libero's side.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:12.24,0:27:14.13,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,{\an8}That was on me!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:12.66,0:27:18.53,Default,Habuka,0,0,0,,More than most teams, \NKarasuno is built around its offense.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:18.53,0:27:24.46,Default,Habuka,0,0,0,,And that focus on the attack is what pushed them to mess up just now.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:24.46,0:27:26.14,Default,Habuka,0,0,0,,Their greatest strength is their weakness.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:26.14,0:27:30.78,Default,Habuka,0,0,0,,We certainly saw Kozume make use of it.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:34.32,0:27:38.84,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,The whole Karasuno team is turning into Shouyou.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:41.74,0:27:44.20,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,May Shorty always be in good health.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:45.14,0:27:46.44,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 5,0:27:50.56,0:27:53.01,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Like, "Why him?"
Dialogue: 5,0:27:53.88,0:27:57.34,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,I'm not all that athletic.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:57.34,0:27:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:58.68,0:28:01.36,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,So, is your high school's team good?
Dialogue: 5,0:28:01.36,0:28:03.75,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Um, I'm not so sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:28:05.09,0:28:09.01,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,They said it used to be good, but then it went downhill.
Dialogue: 5,0:28:10.28,0:28:12.41,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,But only recently...
Dialogue: 5,0:28:14.37,0:28:15.71,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,I'd say it's a pretty good team.
Dialogue: 5,0:28:17.56,0:28:19.67,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,What school do you—
Dialogue: 5,0:28:19.67,0:28:20.72,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Kenma!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:21.92,0:28:22.72,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Kuro.
Dialogue: 5,0:28:23.60,0:28:24.30,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Gotta go.
Dialogue: 5,0:28:24.30,0:28:25.66,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Oh, hey! Kenma!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:28.24,0:28:30.15,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,See you later, Shouyou.
Dialogue: 5,0:28:32.56,0:28:34.11,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,"See you later"?
Dialogue: 5,0:28:37.20,0:28:38.62,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Imagine that.
Dialogue: 5,0:28:38.62,0:28:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:28:40.30,0:28:41.93,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,You don't know that kid, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:28:42.64,0:28:45.54,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Never seen you acting all friendly like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:28:45.85,0:28:47.38,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Took me by surprise.
Dialogue: 5,0:28:48.04,0:28:49.39,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 5,0:28:53.15,0:28:54.17,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Why is that, actually?
Dialogue: 5,0:28:55.21,0:28:58.31,Default,Nekoma Cheering Squad,0,0,0,,{\an8}Go, go, Nekoma! Go, go, Nekoma!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:58.31,0:29:00.14,Default,Bokuto,0,0,0,,Gotta be rough for Karasuno.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:00.14,0:29:01.43,Default,Akaashi,0,0,0,,No doubt.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:02.20,0:29:07.25,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Racking up points with powerful serves would be great and all.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:07.25,0:29:09.35,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,But we're not really at that level.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:09.85,0:29:12.50,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,If you can get points by serving, go for it.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:10.95,0:29:11.56,Default,Nekoma Teammate,0,0,0,,{\an8}Here you go.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:11.56,0:29:12.50,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:12.50,0:29:13.39,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:13.39,0:29:18.10,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,That sounds as wimpy as\N "Anyone who wants seconds, feel free."
Dialogue: 5,0:29:18.10,0:29:20.03,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,It's like you said, Kuro.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:20.03,0:29:23.12,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,There's no perfect strategy to any play.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:23.49,0:29:29.12,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,If Shouyou always scores ten points, \Nwe just need to take two or three of those away.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:29.12,0:29:32.25,Default,Naoi,0,0,0,,Wow, Kenma's way more into this than usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.13,0:29:36.34,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(452,266)\fscx90\fscy90\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Nekoma
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.13,0:29:36.34,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1456,266)\fscx90\fscy90\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Karasuno
Dialogue: 5,0:29:38.64,0:29:40.01,Default,Saeko,0,0,0,,Time to regroup!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:40.48,0:29:42.97,Default,Saeko,0,0,0,,Now we strike back!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:42.97,0:29:44.93,Default,Nishinoya; Azumane; Sawamura; Tanaka,0,0,0,,Bring it!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:47.70,0:29:49.60,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are they targeting number ten again?
Dialogue: 5,0:29:49.60,0:29:50.66,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:51.86,0:29:53.21,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,{\i1}He has no room to run!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:53.21,0:29:56.83,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,{\i1}They forced him to receive it up front so he can't do the fast attack!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:02.38,0:30:05.36,Default,Alisa,0,0,0,,Wow, he cut across the court!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:05.36,0:30:06.87,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,With a broad jump...
Dialogue: 5,0:30:09.74,0:30:11.25,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Nice, Hinata!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:13.13,0:30:17.63,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}He didn't need to use Shouyou for that play.
Dialogue: 5,0:30:17.63,0:30:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 5,0:30:19.41,0:30:23.30,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gonna take more than that to stop our fast attack.
Dialogue: 5,0:30:26.32,0:30:27.53,Default,Fukunaga,0,0,0,,Gave him too much room.
Dialogue: 5,0:30:27.53,0:30:28.98,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Guess so.
Dialogue: 5,0:30:28.98,0:30:32.90,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,I thought it looked good, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:30:34.13,0:30:35.39,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Shouyou.
Dialogue: 5,0:30:35.39,0:30:36.19,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:30:38.11,0:30:40.23,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Stay full of surprises.
Dialogue: 5,0:30:40.78,0:30:42.38,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Let's get one!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:44.42,0:30:46.57,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Wh-What happened, Hinata?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.58,0:30:50.29,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(934,164)\fscx69\frz347.7\fry14\fax0.32\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Nekoma
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.58,0:30:50.29,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1373,262)\fscx32\fscy47\frz348.6\fry36\fax0.3\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur0.9}Karasuno
Dialogue: 5,0:30:49.12,0:30:52.24,Default,Yachi,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we lose one more set, it's all over.
Dialogue: 5,0:30:52.85,0:30:53.82,Default,Yaku BG,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nice receive!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:53.42,0:30:54.79,Default,Bokuto,0,0,0,,"What if they lose?"
Dialogue: 5,0:30:53.82,0:30:54.79,Default,Yamamoto BG,0,0,0,,{\an8}Left!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:55.40,0:30:58.79,Default,Bokuto,0,0,0,,Quit throwing a wet blanket on 'em before it's even over.
Dialogue: 5,0:30:56.80,0:30:58.08,Default,Nekoma BG,0,0,0,,{\an8}All right!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:59.74,0:31:01.90,Default,Bokuto,0,0,0,,Did I use that phrase right?
Dialogue: 5,0:31:01.90,0:31:02.97,Default,Akaashi,0,0,0,,More or less.
Dialogue: 5,0:31:03.66,0:31:07.10,Default,Bokuto,0,0,0,,Forget what's to come. Watch them {\i1}now{\i0}.
Dialogue: 5,0:31:07.61,0:31:10.20,Default,Bokuto,0,0,0,,See how much better we all are.
Dialogue: 5,0:31:11.05,0:31:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it in.
Dialogue: 5,0:31:15.23,0:31:17.29,Default,Nekoma,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:17.29,0:31:18.19,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,Good eye!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:18.67,0:31:21.30,Default,Akaashi,0,0,0,,Bokuto, you're getting overbearing.
Dialogue: 5,0:31:18.67,0:31:19.71,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thanks!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:21.30,0:31:22.01,Default,Bokuto,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:31:22.01,0:31:23.17,Default,Akaashi,0,0,0,,Sorry about him.
Dialogue: 5,0:31:23.17,0:31:24.32,Default,Yachi,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:31:25.07,0:31:27.82,Default,Yachi,0,0,0,,It's hard to look at things in a new way,
Dialogue: 5,0:31:29.57,0:31:31.01,Default,Yachi,0,0,0,,but it feels good!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.04,0:31:34.00,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(452,266)\fscx90\fscy90\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Nekoma
