Dialogue: 5,0:31:34.59,0:31:37.60,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nekoma digs their claws in and are just one point behind yet again.
Dialogue: 5,0:31:39.60,0:31:41.33,Default,Tendo,0,0,0,,Weren't they ahead?
Dialogue: 5,0:31:40.08,0:31:41.84,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hinata is entering the court.
Dialogue: 5,0:31:41.33,0:31:44.95,Default,Tendo,0,0,0,,I go to take a crap and when I get back they've lost the first set!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:41.84,0:31:44.95,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let's see if he'll be able to score once again like earlier.
Dialogue: 5,0:31:44.95,0:31:45.68,Default,Goshiki,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 5,0:31:45.68,0:31:47.07,Default,Tendo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hilarious!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:46.16,0:31:49.39,Default,Goshiki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why don't people watch on their own tablets?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.39,0:31:51.85,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1592,38)\fscx46\fscy46\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&HE1685A&\alpha&HD0&\blur5}Long-awaited Face-off!
