Dialogue: 5,0:31:50.50,0:31:51.85,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}That was a short serve!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:51.85,0:31:54.03,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}Are they aiming for Hinata again?
Dialogue: 5,0:31:53.77,0:31:55.70,Default,Tendo,0,0,0,,Nekoma, was it?
Dialogue: 5,0:31:54.03,0:31:55.44,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tanaka comes in from the left!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:55.44,0:31:56.62,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nekoma connects!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:55.70,0:32:00.31,Default,Tendo,0,0,0,,Definitely never wanna play a team like them, \Nbut they make for great entertainment.
Dialogue: 5,0:31:56.62,0:31:58.85,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yamamoto takes advantage of their space!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:58.85,0:32:00.31,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}Karasuno receives!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.31,0:32:03.86,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1592,38)\fscx46\fscy46\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&HE1685A&\alpha&HD0&\blur5}Long-awaited Face-off!
