Dialogue: 5,0:32:01.34,0:32:02.48,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}They dig it out again!
Dialogue: 5,0:32:02.48,0:32:03.86,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}What tenacious defense!
Dialogue: 5,0:32:03.86,0:32:05.62,Default,Tendo,0,0,0,,Sucks to be Karasuno!
Dialogue: 5,0:32:05.62,0:32:08.19,Default,Tendo,0,0,0,,Bet they're pretty pissed they can't score.
Dialogue: 5,0:32:08.19,0:32:10.66,Default,Tendo,0,0,0,,Think they are? Think it hurts?
Dialogue: 5,0:32:10.66,0:32:11.66,Default,Tendo,0,0,0,,Bet it does.
Dialogue: 5,0:32:11.66,0:32:13.29,Default,Tendo,0,0,0,,Good luck, boys!
Dialogue: 5,0:32:13.29,0:32:14.87,Default,Tendo,0,0,0,,Not that I care.
Dialogue: 5,0:32:14.87,0:32:17.84,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}Karasuno's back with their synchronized offense!
Dialogue: 5,0:32:17.84,0:32:19.70,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hinata comes in from the middle!
Dialogue: 5,0:32:19.70,0:32:22.80,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}But right behind him is Azumane with a lightning-fast back row attack!
Dialogue: 5,0:32:22.80,0:32:25.22,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}But look at that persistence!
Dialogue: 5,0:32:25.22,0:32:26.90,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nekoma continues to persevere!
Dialogue: 5,0:32:26.90,0:32:30.30,Default,Tendo,0,0,0,,They make it sound like the kitty cats are the only ones trying.
Dialogue: 5,0:32:30.30,0:32:32.64,Default,Goshiki,0,0,0,,Nekoma has its persistent defense,
Dialogue: 5,0:32:31.75,0:32:33.04,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}Fukunaga keeps it going!
Dialogue: 5,0:32:32.64,0:32:34.78,Default,Goshiki,0,0,0,,and Karasuno's got persistent offense.
Dialogue: 5,0:32:33.04,0:32:34.78,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yamamoto jumps in and returns the ball!
Dialogue: 5,0:32:34.78,0:32:39.48,Default,Tendo,0,0,0,,Again and again, they have all their spikers play decoy.
Dialogue: 5,0:32:39.86,0:32:43.89,Default,Tendo,0,0,0,,The only difference is whether they're holding the ground or the air.
Dialogue: 5,0:32:40.85,0:32:43.89,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}And Karasuno has another opportunity! Will they finally be able to score?
Dialogue: 5,0:32:43.89,0:32:45.95,Default,Tendo,0,0,0,,Doesn't he get it already?
Dialogue: 5,0:32:43.89,0:32:47.09,Default,Goshiki,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Tendou's tough on the commentators.
Dialogue: 5,0:32:48.28,0:32:56.30,Default,Tendo,0,0,0,,But taking to the air over and over like that the way the crows do is gonna take its toll.
Dialogue: 5,0:32:56.30,0:32:57.71,Default,Tendo,0,0,0,,And worst of all...
Dialogue: 5,0:32:58.17,0:33:00.39,Default,Tendo,0,0,0,,the kitty cats know it.
Dialogue: 5,0:33:02.30,0:33:03.42,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right...
Dialogue: 5,0:33:03.88,0:33:06.77,Default,Nekoma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Time to drag the crows back down to the ground!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:07.63,0:33:09.09,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Here it is! Here it is!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:11.08,0:33:12.80,Default,Tanaka; Azumane; Hinata; Sawamura,0,0,0,,{\i1}Synchronized attack!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:13.70,0:33:18.73,Default,Keishin,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sometimes what looks like the hardest route is actually the easiest.
Dialogue: 5,0:33:25.23,0:33:28.69,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:29.47,0:33:32.29,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wow, that was rough! Well played by Karasuno!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:30.78,0:33:32.29,Default,Tendo,0,0,0,,That's why I hate those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.91,0:33:38.12,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(452,266)\fscx90\fscy90\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Nekoma
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.91,0:33:38.12,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1456,266)\fscx90\fscy90\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Karasuno
Dialogue: 5,0:33:35.80,0:33:38.12,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,How long have we been at this?
Dialogue: 5,0:33:38.48,0:33:40.91,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Feels like the fifth set already.
Dialogue: 5,0:33:40.91,0:33:42.98,Default,Azumane,0,0,0,,Is it not?
Dialogue: 5,0:33:42.98,0:33:45.38,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,It's only the start of the second!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:45.38,0:33:47.38,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Plenty more of the match to play!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:47.38,0:33:49.38,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,Still got a ways to go.
Dialogue: 5,0:33:49.72,0:33:52.17,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Get lost! You guys are like furnaces!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:52.17,0:33:55.38,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,Damn. They keep attacking together.
Dialogue: 5,0:33:52.98,0:33:56.49,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,{\an8}I think this is still better than the interhigh qualifiers.
Dialogue: 5,0:33:55.38,0:33:58.47,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,You forget we're playing Karasuno or something?
Dialogue: 5,0:33:56.49,0:33:58.80,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,{\an8}No, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 5,0:33:58.47,0:33:59.89,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 5,0:33:58.80,0:34:02.46,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,{\an8}Also, there are only three sets in a match,\N so it couldn't possibly be the fifth.
Dialogue: 5,0:33:59.89,0:34:01.99,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,We're wearing them down.
Dialogue: 5,0:34:01.99,0:34:04.36,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,No one has unlimited stamina.
Dialogue: 5,0:34:02.46,0:34:04.36,Default,Azumane,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 5,0:34:05.00,0:34:08.14,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,That goes for us too, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:34:09.20,0:34:10.08,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Kenma.
Dialogue: 5,0:34:11.00,0:34:14.28,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Stop. I don't want to hear it.
Dialogue: 5,0:34:14.59,0:34:16.94,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Let's show 'em what we're made of!
Dialogue: 5,0:34:15.87,0:34:16.94,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\an8}Enough already!
Dialogue: 5,0:34:16.94,0:34:18.51,Default,Naoi,0,0,0,,They've still in good shape.
Dialogue: 5,0:34:19.32,0:34:20.85,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Make it good, Tsukishima!
Dialogue: 5,0:34:21.37,0:34:22.56,Default,Kai,0,0,0,,Fukunaga, move up!
Dialogue: 5,0:34:25.29,0:34:26.04,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,Here's our chance!
Dialogue: 5,0:34:29.53,0:34:31.63,Default,Shimada; Takinoue; Akiteru,0,0,0,,Go for the broad jump!
Dialogue: 5,0:34:36.55,0:34:38.38,Default,Nekoma,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 5,0:34:38.38,0:34:39.02,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:34:40.61,0:34:42.93,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,Scared of me, are ya?
Dialogue: 5,0:34:42.93,0:34:45.39,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,What?! Yeah right!
Dialogue: 5,0:34:45.39,0:34:46.39,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Lev.
Dialogue: 5,0:34:47.23,0:34:48.85,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 5,0:34:48.85,0:34:50.65,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,Chill out, moron.
Dialogue: 5,0:34:51.28,0:34:52.79,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,I'll get the next one!
Dialogue: 5,0:34:52.79,0:34:55.45,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,You just get me the ball!
