Dialogue: 5,0:34:58.62,0:35:02.69,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}They're aiming for the front again, \Nbut the libero Nishinoya has it covered!
Dialogue: 5,0:35:00.12,0:35:00.85,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 5,0:35:02.69,0:35:03.80,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,Get 'em!
Dialogue: 5,0:35:02.69,0:35:03.80,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}The ball goes left.
Dialogue: 5,0:35:03.80,0:35:04.98,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}A powerful straight spike!
Dialogue: 5,0:35:05.58,0:35:07.42,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}Will they be able to get it up?!
Dialogue: 5,0:35:06.28,0:35:08.92,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,Shou isn't having much luck today.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.30,0:35:11.51,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1592,38)\fscx46\fscy46\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&HE1685A&\alpha&HD0&\blur5}Long-awaited Face-off!
