Dialogue: 5,0:35:10.09,0:35:10.98,Default,Sawamura,0,0,0,,Get it!
Dialogue: 5,0:35:12.38,0:35:13.34,Default,Sawamura,0,0,0,,Nice backup!
Dialogue: 5,0:35:14.30,0:35:16.74,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}Karasuno gets it up, but now they're out of position!
Dialogue: 5,0:35:16.74,0:35:20.22,Default,Tendo,0,0,0,,Like that ever stopped them before.
Dialogue: 5,0:35:34.68,0:35:37.70,Default,Lev and Nekoma,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 5,0:35:37.70,0:35:41.16,Default,Nekoma Cheering Squad,0,0,0,,Nice, nice, Haiba! Nice, nice, Haiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.70,0:35:41.16,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(722,789)\fscx42\fscy42\frz4.1\fax-0.08\fnDIST Inking Bold\fsp4.5\b1\c&H19131F&\blur1.3}Connect
Dialogue: 5,0:35:41.16,0:35:44.04,Default,Nekoma Cheering Squad,0,0,0,,Do it again!
Dialogue: 5,0:35:44.75,0:35:46.62,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 5,0:35:46.62,0:35:47.98,Default,Akiteru,0,0,0,,They saw it coming.
Dialogue: 5,0:35:47.98,0:35:49.84,Default,Takinoue,0,0,0,,There were three blockers.
Dialogue: 5,0:35:50.61,0:35:52.80,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,They're climbing their way up!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.80,0:35:55.59,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(452,266)\fscx90\fscy90\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Nekoma
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.80,0:35:55.59,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1456,266)\fscx90\fscy90\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Karasuno
Dialogue: 5,0:35:54.77,0:35:55.59,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Lev.
Dialogue: 5,0:35:56.66,0:36:02.12,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Next time the ball's on their side, \Nif Shouyou is open and running to position,
Dialogue: 5,0:36:02.12,0:36:04.85,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,I want three of you blocking him.
Dialogue: 5,0:36:05.37,0:36:07.65,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,It's probably about time.
Dialogue: 5,0:36:07.65,0:36:11.11,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,How did you know we should put everyone on Hinata?
Dialogue: 5,0:36:11.58,0:36:13.47,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,You're scaring me, Kenma.
Dialogue: 5,0:36:13.47,0:36:17.22,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Notice how he hasn't been on the attack as much?
Dialogue: 5,0:36:17.22,0:36:19.24,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:36:19.24,0:36:22.33,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,When we hit him with a good serve.
Dialogue: 5,0:36:22.33,0:36:24.13,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 5,0:36:26.00,0:36:28.04,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,They're not just making him receive.
Dialogue: 5,0:36:28.77,0:36:30.58,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,They're using me too.
Dialogue: 5,0:36:32.12,0:36:37.93,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,At the start of the set, Shouyou bumped it up and then ran for the broad jump, yeah?
Dialogue: 5,0:36:38.24,0:36:41.56,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,But next time on that rotation, and again now...
Dialogue: 5,0:36:41.56,0:36:46.73,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,They used me to get in the way and keep him off the right side.
Dialogue: 5,0:36:47.32,0:36:49.41,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,I thought it was just a fluke at first.
Dialogue: 5,0:36:50.16,0:36:52.44,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,But it's definitely intentional.
Dialogue: 5,0:36:53.67,0:36:55.96,Default,Sawamura,0,0,0,,Working hard to keep him down...
Dialogue: 5,0:36:58.09,0:37:03.55,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Shouyou loves to jump, so when he can't,\N he'll get frustrated and panic.
Dialogue: 5,0:37:04.92,0:37:08.40,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,That overpowered spike out of bounds is proof.
Dialogue: 5,0:37:10.21,0:37:14.71,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,And like any good setter, he doesn't want to have that hang around in a spiker's mind.
Dialogue: 5,0:37:15.43,0:37:20.29,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,So I knew the next time he was ready,\N Shouyou would get the ball.
Dialogue: 5,0:37:22.53,0:37:24.21,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,You're really scaring me, Kenma.
Dialogue: 5,0:37:24.21,0:37:25.27,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 5,0:37:25.27,0:37:26.26,Default,Kai,0,0,0,,And me.
Dialogue: 5,0:37:27.62,0:37:29.29,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,That's all we need.
Dialogue: 5,0:37:29.29,0:37:34.55,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Like I said, there's no perfect way to stop an attack.
Dialogue: 5,0:37:34.55,0:37:39.71,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,With Karasuno, we just need to steal a few points they'd normally get.
Dialogue: 5,0:37:39.71,0:37:45.53,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,That'll stress them out enough to see them start to slip up.
Dialogue: 5,0:37:45.53,0:37:48.73,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,One slip-up turns to two, then three.
Dialogue: 5,0:37:50.41,0:37:52.17,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,It's about paths, not points.
Dialogue: 5,0:37:53.24,0:37:55.44,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,We block him from moving.
Dialogue: 5,0:37:57.90,0:38:01.39,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Stop his approach, and we clip his wings.
Dialogue: 5,0:38:17.77,0:38:19.25,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Kenma!
Dialogue: 5,0:38:20.16,0:38:22.07,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,What now? You hungry or something?
Dialogue: 5,0:38:22.69,0:38:25.71,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Your mom gave me some shrimp crackers. Want some?
Dialogue: 5,0:38:25.71,0:38:30.03,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Beating a game feels worse than getting a game over in it.
Dialogue: 5,0:38:30.03,0:38:30.76,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:38:32.39,0:38:34.08,Default,Lev and Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 5,0:38:36.50,0:38:37.83,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 5,0:38:37.83,0:38:38.65,Default,Keishin,0,0,0,,Kageyama.
Dialogue: 5,0:38:43.34,0:38:45.41,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Give us another good one, Fukunaga!
Dialogue: 5,0:38:52.70,0:38:53.62,Default,Azumane,0,0,0,,Left!
Dialogue: 5,0:38:56.04,0:38:58.15,Default,Tanaka; Nishinoya; Sawamura; Azumane; Hinata,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 5,0:38:58.47,0:39:00.47,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Nice one, Asahi!
Dialogue: 5,0:39:00.47,0:39:01.93,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it!
Dialogue: 5,0:39:04.86,0:39:07.67,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once they can't use him as a decoy anymore,
Dialogue: 5,0:39:07.67,0:39:10.40,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}it gets much easier for us to block.
Dialogue: 5,0:39:11.56,0:39:16.07,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if we don't make him receive or block his path,
Dialogue: 5,0:39:16.07,0:39:18.28,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}we just need him second-guessing.
Dialogue: 5,0:39:18.89,0:39:22.53,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Should I get the ball or leave it for them?"
Dialogue: 5,0:39:23.33,0:39:27.57,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's much more focused on the receive than ever.
Dialogue: 5,0:39:29.95,0:39:30.76,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,I touched it!
Dialogue: 5,0:39:31.46,0:39:36.19,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shorty's never seemed so out of the play before.
Dialogue: 5,0:39:37.13,0:39:40.19,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's going to try and do it all.
Dialogue: 5,0:39:40.49,0:39:43.34,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Receive. Get a running start.
Dialogue: 5,0:39:42.32,0:39:43.97,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let's score here!
Dialogue: 5,0:39:43.34,0:39:46.53,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,{\i1}But trying doesn't mean doing.
Dialogue: 5,0:39:46.53,0:39:48.74,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,Don't forget about me!
Dialogue: 5,0:39:53.91,0:39:56.37,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 5,0:39:56.37,0:39:59.08,Default,Nekoma,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nice spike, Haiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.37,0:39:59.08,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(722,789)\fscx42\fscy42\frz4.1\fax-0.08\fnDIST Inking Bold\fsp4.5\b1\c&H19131F&\blur1.3}Connect
Dialogue: 5,0:39:59.08,0:40:00.98,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,They can pull off back row attacks?
Dialogue: 5,0:39:59.45,0:40:05.38,Default,Nekoma,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nice, nice, Haiba! Push it, push it, Haiba! Do it again!
Dialogue: 5,0:40:00.98,0:40:02.49,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,I mean, it's Lev.
Dialogue: 5,0:40:02.49,0:40:05.38,Default,Sawamura,0,0,0,,Make a mental note and get back in position!
Dialogue: 5,0:40:06.40,0:40:08.73,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right! Here comes another!
Dialogue: 5,0:40:09.26,0:40:10.25,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,That's going out!
Dialogue: 5,0:40:11.31,0:40:12.91,Default,Karasuno,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.48,0:40:16.56,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(452,266)\fscx90\fscy90\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Nekoma
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.48,0:40:16.56,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1456,266)\fscx90\fscy90\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Karasuno
Dialogue: 5,0:40:15.63,0:40:16.56,Default,Takinoue,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 5,0:40:16.92,0:40:19.65,Default,Takinoue,0,0,0,,Hinata ended up in the back row without scoring a single point.
Dialogue: 5,0:40:19.65,0:40:21.36,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Give us a good serve, Hinata!
Dialogue: 5,0:40:21.66,0:40:23.18,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 5,0:40:23.18,0:40:24.61,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 5,0:40:26.34,0:40:28.07,Default,Nekoma,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 5,0:40:28.56,0:40:30.78,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,You're fun to play against.
Dialogue: 5,0:40:30.78,0:40:32.50,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,Let's get this point!
Dialogue: 5,0:40:34.76,0:40:36.37,Default,Reserves,0,0,0,,Nice receive!
Dialogue: 5,0:40:37.09,0:40:39.46,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,This is our match where there's no extra lives!
Dialogue: 5,0:40:39.75,0:40:40.98,Default,Reserves,0,0,0,,Yeah! Go!
Dialogue: 5,0:40:40.98,0:40:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 5,0:40:42.48,0:40:44.45,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,This is just a time waster.
Dialogue: 5,0:40:45.34,0:40:48.47,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,It was just the same old thing.
Dialogue: 5,0:40:52.93,0:40:55.17,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Stay full of surprises.
Dialogue: 5,0:41:03.52,0:41:04.55,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,Shouyou!
Dialogue: 5,0:41:05.11,0:41:06.74,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,You're up.
Dialogue: 5,0:41:06.74,0:41:08.03,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 5,0:41:08.60,0:41:10.74,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,All right! Let's hype things up!
Dialogue: 5,0:41:11.84,0:41:15.08,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,Wow... I didn't see this coming.
Dialogue: 5,0:41:15.99,0:41:18.28,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,Big events like this don't happen every day.
Dialogue: 5,0:41:18.28,0:41:21.62,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,We can't go packing it up after just two sets!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.46,0:41:24.67,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(795,159)\fscx90\fscy90\frz349.5\fax0.19\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1.3}Nekoma
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.46,0:41:24.67,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1536,298)\fscx53\fscy53\frz349.5\fax0.19\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1.2}Karasuno
Dialogue: 5,0:41:26.38,0:41:27.73,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,Fukunaga!
Dialogue: 5,0:41:30.80,0:41:32.01,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,Nice receive!
Dialogue: 5,0:41:31.13,0:41:32.01,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,{\an8}All right!
Dialogue: 5,0:41:34.47,0:41:36.14,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,{\i1}The setter stepped back!
Dialogue: 5,0:41:36.50,0:41:38.10,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,{\i1}Five attackers?!
Dialogue: 5,0:41:38.38,0:41:39.81,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Got the run-up I need!
Dialogue: 5,0:41:40.64,0:41:42.06,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}His troublesome speed...
Dialogue: 5,0:41:49.64,0:41:50.78,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Got the run-up—
Dialogue: 5,0:41:53.66,0:41:57.58,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}His jumps that get him up there with 190-cm tall blockers...
Dialogue: 5,0:41:57.58,0:41:58.72,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 5,0:42:03.23,0:42:05.59,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Got the run-up I need!
Dialogue: 5,0:42:06.12,0:42:11.05,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once he's one step behind, \Nit's too late, and he's all but out.
Dialogue: 5,0:42:11.88,0:42:15.26,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Giving it 99% isn't enough.
Dialogue: 5,0:42:17.24,0:42:17.97,Default,Azumane,0,0,0,,It's coming over!
Dialogue: 5,0:42:18.59,0:42:19.48,Default,Azumane,0,0,0,,Let's score here!
Dialogue: 5,0:42:19.48,0:42:20.43,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 5,0:42:20.43,0:42:22.39,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Got the run-up I—
Dialogue: 5,0:42:25.89,0:42:29.57,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because if he can't jump with 100% effort...
Dialogue: 5,0:42:30.28,0:42:33.24,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kageyama isn't interested.
Dialogue: 5,0:42:40.41,0:42:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nice, nice, Haiba! Nice, nice, Haiba! Do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.41,0:42:43.87,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(722,789)\fscx42\fscy42\frz4.1\fax-0.08\fnDIST Inking Bold\fsp4.5\b1\c&H19131F&\blur1.3}Connect
Dialogue: 5,0:42:43.87,0:42:46.84,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 5,0:42:47.18,0:42:48.54,Default,Yachi,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 5,0:42:48.54,0:42:50.86,Default,Yachi,0,0,0,,They tried so hard too...
Dialogue: 5,0:42:50.86,0:42:52.42,Default,Akaashi,0,0,0,,Just bad luck.
Dialogue: 5,0:42:53.12,0:42:56.96,Default,Takeda,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did this have to happen right now?
Dialogue: 5,0:42:56.96,0:42:58.48,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:42:58.48,0:42:59.60,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 5,0:42:59.60,0:43:00.56,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 5,0:43:01.49,0:43:04.05,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything's going according to plan,
Dialogue: 5,0:43:05.22,0:43:07.53,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,{\i1}so what's with the face?
Dialogue: 5,0:43:07.53,0:43:12.24,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're telling me you wanna see him fly while you rip out all his feathers?
Dialogue: 5,0:43:13.87,0:43:16.63,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're a real pain in the butt.
Dialogue: 5,0:43:22.02,0:43:23.29,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it too risky?
Dialogue: 5,0:43:24.04,0:43:25.92,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it worth a shot?
Dialogue: 5,0:43:26.73,0:43:29.17,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is Hinata even up for it?
Dialogue: 5,0:43:33.81,0:43:36.84,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to break down the walls in front of our spikers.
Dialogue: 5,0:43:37.80,0:43:39.41,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's a setter's job.
Dialogue: 5,0:43:42.12,0:43:45.18,Default,Washio,0,0,0,,Without that setter, Kageyama,
Dialogue: 5,0:43:45.18,0:43:47.35,Default,Washio,0,0,0,,I can't say that I sense any worth in you.
Dialogue: 5,0:43:51.66,0:43:52.54,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,Hinata!
Dialogue: 5,0:43:53.58,0:43:55.03,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,Nice receive.
Dialogue: 5,0:43:55.03,0:43:57.20,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,Keep that up for me.
Dialogue: 5,0:43:58.48,0:43:59.54,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:44:02.84,0:44:05.12,Default,Nekoma Student A,0,0,0,,What's number ten on the black team in there for?
Dialogue: 5,0:44:05.75,0:44:08.30,Default,Nekoma Student A,0,0,0,,He's tiny and doesn't really get many shots in.
Dialogue: 5,0:44:08.30,0:44:10.30,Default,Nekoma Student A,0,0,0,,Why do they keep him in?
Dialogue: 5,0:44:10.30,0:44:13.09,Default,Nekoma Student B,0,0,0,,He was pretty good in the first set.
Dialogue: 5,0:44:13.60,0:44:14.92,Default,Nekoma Student A,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:44:14.92,0:44:19.55,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,{\i1}He can't do anything 'cause our team's making sure he can't!
Dialogue: 5,0:44:20.25,0:44:21.44,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,Give us a good one!
Dialogue: 5,0:44:28.06,0:44:30.48,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}It must be tough, Shouyou.
Dialogue: 5,0:44:31.58,0:44:35.89,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kenma's trying to make my own receives keep me down.
Dialogue: 5,0:44:36.84,0:44:40.94,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}The more he thinks about it, the more he wants an answer.
Dialogue: 5,0:44:41.76,0:44:46.26,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{\i1}How can I receive the ball and still get room to run up?
Dialogue: 5,0:44:47.50,0:44:51.25,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}The more frustrated he gets,\N the more shortcuts he'll look for.
Dialogue: 5,0:44:52.63,0:44:54.36,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{\i1}What now?
Dialogue: 5,0:44:54.36,0:44:55.97,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{\i1}What can I do?
Dialogue: 5,0:44:58.28,0:45:00.35,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go on and flail around.
Dialogue: 5,0:45:02.10,0:45:03.45,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Give us a good one!
Dialogue: 5,0:45:05.13,0:45:05.88,Default,Sawamura,0,0,0,,Up front!
Dialogue: 5,0:45:11.01,0:45:14.11,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Going for the receive is keeping me down.
Dialogue: 5,0:45:16.26,0:45:17.79,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Game over.
Dialogue: 5,0:45:19.91,0:45:21.30,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess this is it.
Dialogue: 5,0:45:26.97,0:45:28.71,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{\i1}But even still,
Dialogue: 5,0:45:29.14,0:45:31.40,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't just go for one or the other!
Dialogue: 5,0:45:32.39,0:45:35.15,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{\i1}No receive means no spike!
Dialogue: 5,0:45:35.15,0:45:37.97,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can't play volleyball if we don't keep the ball up!
Dialogue: 5,0:45:38.45,0:45:40.47,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we want to score...
Dialogue: 5,0:45:41.06,0:45:42.22,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{\i1}there aren't any shortcuts!
Dialogue: 5,0:45:47.17,0:45:48.20,Default,Keishin,0,0,0,,Kageyama.
Dialogue: 5,0:45:49.84,0:45:51.40,Default,Keishin,0,0,0,,Be brave out there.
Dialogue: 5,0:45:53.50,0:45:54.58,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 5,0:45:54.58,0:45:56.32,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:45:57.14,0:45:59.19,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pave the way for him!
Dialogue: 5,0:46:00.28,0:46:01.24,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,High ball!
Dialogue: 5,0:46:04.70,0:46:05.62,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go on, then!
Dialogue: 5,0:46:07.00,0:46:07.79,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jump!
Dialogue: 5,0:46:10.75,0:46:12.71,Default,Tendo; Goshiki; Bokuto; Akaashi; Daisho; Akane,0,0,0,,{\i1}High to the middle?!
Dialogue: 5,0:46:22.93,0:46:24.64,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Got my run-up!
Dialogue: 5,0:46:25.18,0:46:27.41,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did he set it that high on purpose?
Dialogue: 5,0:46:28.58,0:46:29.68,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}While we have three blockers?
Dialogue: 5,0:46:29.68,0:46:35.56,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Plus, this isn't an in-sync fast attack, and high sets are hard for most people.
Dialogue: 5,0:46:35.56,0:46:41.32,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shouyou has always worked with a technically-sound setter and only pulled off quicks, so there's no way...
Dialogue: 5,0:46:42.44,0:46:45.03,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,I know that you can jump higher.
Dialogue: 5,0:46:45.03,0:46:50.14,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,And when you make those jumps, \Nyou hear the sound of your feet kicking off the floor.
Dialogue: 5,0:47:11.93,0:47:13.48,Default,Hinata and Kageyama,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.48,0:47:18.90,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1460,940)\fscx80\fscy87\fnLeviBrush\c&HD6D3D3&\alpha&HE0&\blur7.5}Fly
Dialogue: 1,0:47:13.48,0:47:18.90,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1460,940)\fscx80\fscy87\fnLeviBrush\c&HD6D3D3&\blur1}Fly
Dialogue: 5,0:47:15.60,0:47:20.74,Default,Karasuno Cheering Squad,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nice, nice, Shouyou! Push it, push it, Shouyou! Do it again!
Dialogue: 5,0:47:19.66,0:47:22.61,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that {\i0}was{\i1} on purpose?
Dialogue: 5,0:47:22.61,0:47:24.36,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even when Shouyou's biggest strength is speed?
Dialogue: 5,0:47:24.36,0:47:27.20,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,{\an8}Did I just see you jump higher than ever?
Dialogue: 5,0:47:25.24,0:47:28.65,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}And he can hit those high sets too?
Dialogue: 5,0:47:27.20,0:47:30.23,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm right in the middle of perfecting the "bam" jump!
Dialogue: 5,0:47:31.64,0:47:34.37,Default,Keishin,0,0,0,,Did you see that jump?
Dialogue: 5,0:47:36.04,0:47:37.40,Default,Akaashi,0,0,0,,Talk about height.
Dialogue: 5,0:47:39.79,0:47:42.01,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,Not a bad jump.
Dialogue: 5,0:47:43.47,0:47:46.29,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,That set was {\i1}amazing{\i0}.
Dialogue: 5,0:47:48.07,0:47:49.39,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,I was complimenting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.35,0:47:56.81,signs,,0,0,0,,{=5}{\move(1692,272,1709.46,247.55,19,5441)\fscx61\fscy61\fnIwata Mincho Old Pro-En H\alpha&HB0&\blur7.5\c&HFEFCFC&}Over the \Nblockers...
Dialogue: 1,0:47:51.35,0:47:56.81,signs,,0,0,0,,{=5}{\move(1692,272,1709.46,247.55,19,5441)\fscx61\fscy61\fnIwata Mincho Old Pro-En H\blur0.85\c&HFEFCFC&}Over the \Nblockers...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.35,0:47:56.81,signs,,0,0,0,,{=6}{\move(1659,802,1670.26,835.63,19,5441)\fscx61\fscy61\frz22.91\fnIwata Mincho Old Pro-En H\alpha&HB0&\blur7.5\c&HFEFCFC&}Right, in the\N air longer
Dialogue: 1,0:47:51.35,0:47:56.81,signs,,0,0,0,,{=6}{\move(1659,802,1670.26,835.63,19,5441)\fscx61\fscy61\frz22.91\fnIwata Mincho Old Pro-En H\blur0.85\c&HFEFCFC&}Right, in the\N air longer
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.35,0:47:56.81,signs,,0,0,0,,{=7}{\move(1385,965,1415.94,985.77,19,5441)\fscx61\fscy61\frz-6.82\fnIwata Mincho Old Pro-En H\alpha&HB0&\blur7.5\c&HFEFCFC&}Shouyou\N can hit\N high sets\N too
Dialogue: 1,0:47:51.35,0:47:56.81,signs,,0,0,0,,{=7}{\move(1385,965,1415.94,985.77,19,5441)\fscx61\fscy61\frz-6.82\fnIwata Mincho Old Pro-En H\blur0.85\c&HFEFCFC&}Shouyou\N can hit\N high sets\N too
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.35,0:47:56.81,signs,,0,0,0,,{=9}{\move(355,778,341.83,818.41,19,5441)\fscx61\fscy61\frz31.72\fnIwata Mincho Old Pro-En H\alpha&HB0&\blur7.5\c&HFEFCFC&}That wasn't \Nlike the blocks \Nthat barely\N keep up...
Dialogue: 1,0:47:51.35,0:47:56.81,signs,,0,0,0,,{=9}{\move(355,778,341.83,818.41,19,5441)\fscx61\fscy61\frz31.72\fnIwata Mincho Old Pro-En H\blur0.85\c&HFEFCFC&}That wasn't \Nlike the blocks \Nthat barely\N keep up...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.35,0:47:56.81,signs,,0,0,0,,{=10}{\move(136,1009,194.99,1009.13,19,5441)\fscx61\fscy61\fnIwata Mincho Old Pro-En H\alpha&HB0&\blur7.5\c&HFEFCFC&}The timing's\N totally different
Dialogue: 1,0:47:51.35,0:47:56.81,signs,,0,0,0,,{=10}{\move(136,1009,194.99,1009.13,19,5441)\fscx61\fscy61\fnIwata Mincho Old Pro-En H\blur0.85\c&HFEFCFC&}The timing's\N totally different
Dialogue: 5,0:47:55.35,0:47:56.81,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right.
Dialogue: 5,0:47:57.35,0:48:01.88,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}If magic and status effects are blocked and don't work,
Dialogue: 5,0:48:01.88,0:48:05.78,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}you just have to go all-in on physical attacks, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:48:08.25,0:48:10.50,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,{\i1}He doesn't need me to say a thing.
Dialogue: 5,0:48:11.58,0:48:13.41,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Kageyama, you got this!
Dialogue: 5,0:48:16.04,0:48:16.83,Default,Someone,0,0,0,,It's out!
Dialogue: 5,0:48:20.01,0:48:21.38,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Close one.
Dialogue: 5,0:48:24.53,0:48:26.09,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,It's Inuoka!
Dialogue: 5,0:48:28.11,0:48:30.21,Default,Shimada,0,0,0,,It's their quick number seven!
Dialogue: 5,0:48:30.21,0:48:32.68,Default,Takinoue,0,0,0,,They're putting up defenses already.
Dialogue: 5,0:48:34.14,0:48:37.02,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Double shields: equipped!
Dialogue: 5,0:48:38.04,0:48:40.21,Default,Inuoka,0,0,0,,So ready for this!
Dialogue: 5,0:48:42.86,0:48:45.25,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,Their defense was solid enough already.
Dialogue: 5,0:48:45.25,0:48:48.06,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,And now they put up even bigger walls?!
Dialogue: 5,0:48:48.06,0:48:50.57,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,Shouldn't that be against the rules or something?!
Dialogue: 5,0:48:51.58,0:48:56.11,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,If Shouyou gets another set like that again, \Nhold back on your block a bit.
Dialogue: 5,0:48:56.11,0:48:57.23,Default,Lev and Inuoka,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 5,0:48:57.23,0:49:00.51,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,He gets more air time than us.
Dialogue: 5,0:49:00.51,0:49:01.63,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 5,0:49:05.07,0:49:05.80,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 5,0:49:05.07,0:49:05.80,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,{\an8}Daichi!
Dialogue: 5,0:49:05.80,0:49:06.73,Default,Sawamura,0,0,0,,On it!
Dialogue: 5,0:49:08.06,0:49:09.59,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nice receive!
Dialogue: 5,0:49:08.35,0:49:09.59,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}They worked it out.
Dialogue: 5,0:49:16.18,0:49:17.12,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{\an8}Huh?!
Dialogue: 5,0:49:16.18,0:49:17.89,Default,Inuoka,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 5,0:49:19.04,0:49:21.42,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Here comes another in the middle!
Dialogue: 5,0:49:22.15,0:49:22.99,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again?
Dialogue: 5,0:49:25.56,0:49:27.32,Default,Inuoka and Lev,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hold back a bit...
Dialogue: 5,0:49:27.32,0:49:28.95,Default,Inuoka and Lev,0,0,0,,{\i1}And...
Dialogue: 5,0:49:33.02,0:49:34.01,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,In the back!
Dialogue: 5,0:49:34.73,0:49:36.69,Default,Karasuno,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:49:37.76,0:49:40.47,Default,Takinoue,0,0,0,,Hinata was aiming for their fingertips!
Dialogue: 5,0:49:40.47,0:49:44.21,Default,Shimada,0,0,0,,Yeah, defenders must hate him for it.
Dialogue: 5,0:49:40.96,0:49:44.21,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,{\an8}That was awesome, Hinata!
Dialogue: 5,0:49:46.12,0:49:48.33,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}What comes next?
Dialogue: 5,0:49:49.22,0:49:50.68,Default,Saeko,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.68,0:49:52.64,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(452,266)\fscx90\fscy90\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Nekoma
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.68,0:49:52.64,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1456,266)\fscx90\fscy90\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Karasuno
Dialogue: 5,0:49:51.08,0:49:52.64,Default,Saeko,0,0,0,,Just one more point!
Dialogue: 5,0:49:52.64,0:49:54.52,Default,Sawamura,0,0,0,,Get 'em, Hinata!
Dialogue: 5,0:49:54.52,0:49:55.62,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,Move up!
Dialogue: 5,0:49:56.10,0:49:57.81,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will it be Kuroo?
Dialogue: 5,0:49:56.45,0:49:57.81,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Center!
Dialogue: 5,0:49:57.81,0:49:58.59,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,{\i1}No!
Dialogue: 5,0:50:02.90,0:50:03.86,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,I touched it!
Dialogue: 5,0:50:03.86,0:50:05.61,Default,Sugawara; Yamaguchi; Nishinoya; Yachi; Saeko,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 5,0:50:06.00,0:50:09.03,Default,Tsukishima; Hinata; Sawamura; Azumane; Tanaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}Full-team synchronized attack!
Dialogue: 5,0:50:11.76,0:50:12.70,Default,Kuro,0,0,0,,I touched it!
Dialogue: 5,0:50:12.70,0:50:14.41,Default,Nekoma reserves,0,0,0,,Here's our chance!
Dialogue: 5,0:50:14.69,0:50:16.12,Default,Kuroo; Inuoka; Yamamoto; Fukunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}Synchronized attack!
Dialogue: 5,0:50:27.46,0:50:28.38,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it.
Dialogue: 5,0:50:29.03,0:50:32.01,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}We face a new Shouyou every single time.
Dialogue: 5,0:50:32.01,0:50:33.49,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,In the back!
Dialogue: 5,0:50:37.32,0:50:38.26,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,Shouyou!
Dialogue: 5,0:50:38.26,0:50:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice job!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.68,0:50:42.14,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(498,268)\fscx66\fscy66\fax-0.13\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1.1}N{\fax-0.124}e{\fax-0.118}k{\fax-0.112}o{\fax-0.106}m{\fax-0.1}a
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.68,0:50:42.14,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1410,266)\fscx66\fscy66\fax0.11\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1.1}K{\fax0.119}a{\fax0.127}r{\fax0.136}a{\fax0.144}s{\fax0.153}u{\fax0.161}n{\fax0.17}o
Dialogue: 5,0:50:42.52,0:50:45.22,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,I thought that was a damn good straight spike!
Dialogue: 5,0:50:45.22,0:50:47.71,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,It was.
Dialogue: 5,0:50:47.71,0:50:50.34,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,What's up with your number ten?!
Dialogue: 5,0:50:50.34,0:50:51.86,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,I'm not sure either.
Dialogue: 5,0:50:53.48,0:50:56.25,Default,Alisa,0,0,0,,Akane, we're just getting started!
Dialogue: 5,0:50:56.89,0:50:59.39,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know. It's just frustrating.
Dialogue: 5,0:50:59.39,0:51:03.06,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,I know that doesn't make sense, but it just is!
Dialogue: 5,0:51:03.72,0:51:06.50,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,They scored on the receive.
Dialogue: 5,0:51:06.50,0:51:09.04,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,That's one set each.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.50,0:51:11.21,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(343,315)\fscx69\fscy91\frz10.76\fax-0.25\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Nekoma
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.50,0:51:11.21,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1240,150)\fscx102\fscy135\frz10.76\fax-0.25\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Karasuno
Dialogue: 5,0:51:09.04,0:51:13.11,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,But the team who wins the second set has the advantage.
Dialogue: 5,0:51:13.11,0:51:16.47,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,And now number ten is back to normal.
Dialogue: 5,0:51:17.17,0:51:22.38,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought Kageyama wouldn't want anything to do with Shouyou not at 100%.
Dialogue: 5,0:51:23.18,0:51:27.31,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if Shouyou's not at 100%, he'll set him up so he is.
Dialogue: 5,0:51:30.39,0:51:32.53,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,Like a pair of monsters.
Dialogue: 5,0:51:33.82,0:51:36.82,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,Quit acting all smug over dumb luck.
Dialogue: 5,0:51:36.82,0:51:38.74,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Ever try saying something nice?!
Dialogue: 5,0:51:38.74,0:51:41.46,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,You weren't focused out there again, were you?
Dialogue: 5,0:51:41.46,0:51:43.50,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,Let's give it to 'em! C'mon!
Dialogue: 5,0:51:43.90,0:51:46.23,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,I'll get us 20 points!
Dialogue: 5,0:51:46.23,0:51:48.77,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,You guys go ahead and get the other five.
Dialogue: 5,0:51:48.77,0:51:50.37,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Lemme tell you something.
Dialogue: 5,0:51:51.13,0:51:53.12,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,When you're working out...
Dialogue: 5,0:51:53.12,0:51:55.76,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Instead of doing 100 normal sit-ups,
Dialogue: 5,0:51:55.76,0:52:00.33,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,it's better to use weights that leave you barely able to do ten.
Dialogue: 5,0:52:03.76,0:52:05.23,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,The hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 5,0:52:05.23,0:52:06.29,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:52:06.29,0:52:09.63,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,It's not the number that matters?!
Dialogue: 5,0:52:09.63,0:52:11.02,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Which means... what?
Dialogue: 5,0:52:11.02,0:52:14.74,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,One heavy points is better than 20 normal ones?
Dialogue: 5,0:52:14.74,0:52:15.74,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Nod.
Dialogue: 5,0:52:15.74,0:52:17.20,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,Don't "nod" out loud.
Dialogue: 5,0:52:17.20,0:52:20.20,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,What the heck's a "heavy point"? Get 20!
Dialogue: 5,0:52:23.28,0:52:25.85,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, did you know? When you work out...
Dialogue: 5,0:52:24.10,0:52:25.17,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:52:25.17,0:52:27.46,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,You gotta be more excited than that!
Dialogue: 5,0:52:27.46,0:52:28.78,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,{\an8}What, Shibayama?
Dialogue: 5,0:52:28.05,0:52:31.61,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,That straight spike was awesome, yeah?
Dialogue: 5,0:52:28.78,0:52:30.55,Default,Shibayama,0,0,0,,{\an8}No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 5,0:52:32.34,0:52:33.66,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,When'd you master that?
Dialogue: 5,0:52:33.66,0:52:34.42,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Thanks, man!
Dialogue: 5,0:52:34.88,0:52:36.62,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,{\an8}All right!
Dialogue: 5,0:52:35.31,0:52:36.62,Default,Naoi,0,0,0,,He's good.
Dialogue: 5,0:52:36.62,0:52:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 5,0:52:37.88,0:52:41.01,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Watch your timing with Shorty out there.
Dialogue: 5,0:52:41.01,0:52:42.47,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,The last one was good.
Dialogue: 5,0:52:42.47,0:52:43.77,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,I already told them.
Dialogue: 5,0:52:43.77,0:52:45.18,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Did you, now?!
Dialogue: 5,0:52:46.87,0:52:48.05,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:52:48.05,0:52:50.06,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Just thought you sure talk a lot.
Dialogue: 5,0:52:50.06,0:52:51.82,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Talk about a sucker punch.
Dialogue: 5,0:52:53.06,0:52:56.54,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kuro is good at motivating people.
Dialogue: 5,0:52:57.85,0:52:59.30,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Always has been.
Dialogue: 5,0:53:03.91,0:53:06.62,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,That was close! Put your arms like this.
Dialogue: 5,0:53:06.62,0:53:09.54,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,Hit it here and you'll be good.
Dialogue: 5,0:53:09.54,0:53:11.94,Default,Kid Kenma,0,0,0,,Why not find someone who plays already?
Dialogue: 5,0:53:11.94,0:53:14.34,Default,Kid Kenma,0,0,0,,It's gotta be boring playing with a newbie.
Dialogue: 5,0:53:14.34,0:53:15.97,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,It's not!
Dialogue: 5,0:53:15.97,0:53:18.33,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,You pick it up quick! And you're smart!
Dialogue: 5,0:53:18.33,0:53:20.05,Default,Kid Kenma,0,0,0,,Y-You think?
Dialogue: 5,0:53:20.92,0:53:25.95,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kuro moved in next door and invited me to play for the first time.
Dialogue: 5,0:53:27.11,0:53:30.39,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was doomed the moment I let his compliment go to my head.
Dialogue: 5,0:53:30.39,0:53:33.58,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,H-Hey, you free on Saturday?
Dialogue: 5,0:53:43.41,0:53:45.36,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,Hiya. Come to watch?
Dialogue: 5,0:53:45.36,0:53:46.82,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,Wanna play?
Dialogue: 5,0:53:46.82,0:53:47.61,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:53:48.85,0:53:49.79,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 5,0:53:50.77,0:53:52.34,Default,Kid A,0,0,0,,Dang it!
Dialogue: 5,0:53:52.34,0:53:53.39,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 5,0:53:54.48,0:53:56.25,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,Wow, nice work!
Dialogue: 5,0:53:59.60,0:54:01.70,Default,Kid Kenma,0,0,0,,That's way cooler.
Dialogue: 5,0:54:01.70,0:54:03.30,Default,Kid Kenma,0,0,0,,You're not gonna do that?
Dialogue: 5,0:54:04.70,0:54:06.14,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,That's called a spike!
Dialogue: 5,0:54:06.14,0:54:07.77,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,Super cool, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:54:08.69,0:54:12.14,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,Can't do that unless you're tall, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:54:12.14,0:54:14.48,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,You could always lower the net.
Dialogue: 5,0:54:15.17,0:54:18.94,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's better to get a taste of it first?
Dialogue: 5,0:54:19.79,0:54:22.84,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,Easier to get good when you're having fun, you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:54:30.16,0:54:31.41,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 5,0:54:45.42,0:54:47.48,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,I hit it!
Dialogue: 5,0:54:47.48,0:54:49.83,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was the most minor of things.
Dialogue: 5,0:54:47.49,0:54:50.38,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nice spike! That was perfect!
Dialogue: 5,0:54:49.83,0:54:53.85,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he would never forget that day.
Dialogue: 5,0:54:50.38,0:54:51.96,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 5,0:54:52.78,0:54:54.14,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{\an8}Want another go?
Dialogue: 5,0:54:53.85,0:54:55.38,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could just tell.
Dialogue: 5,0:54:54.14,0:54:54.85,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes!
Dialogue: 5,0:55:02.91,0:55:05.20,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,Kenma! Let's play volleyball!
Dialogue: 5,0:55:05.49,0:55:07.12,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,Kenma! Volleyball time!
Dialogue: 5,0:55:07.49,0:55:09.33,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,Kenma!
Dialogue: 5,0:55:11.04,0:55:13.01,Default,Kid Kenma,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.50,0:55:18.21,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(735,357)\fscx115\fscy115\frz4.96\fnHandwritten Crystal v2\fsp2\c&H3F3F3F&\alpha&HD0&\blur7.5}Brazil\N vs. USA
Dialogue: 1,0:55:16.50,0:55:18.21,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(735,357)\fscx115\fscy115\frz4.96\fnHandwritten Crystal v2\fsp2\c&H3F3F3F&\blur1}Brazil\N vs. USA
Dialogue: 5,0:55:20.95,0:55:22.17,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,Dang it!
Dialogue: 5,0:55:24.57,0:55:25.80,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 5,0:55:30.80,0:55:33.10,Default,Kid Kenma,0,0,0,,Did you see that? Did you?!
Dialogue: 5,0:55:33.10,0:55:38.36,Default,Kid Kenma,0,0,0,,He looked right, but just when you thought you knew, he sent it to the left!
Dialogue: 5,0:55:39.36,0:55:43.48,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,It stopped raining, so can we stop watching and go out?
Dialogue: 5,0:55:43.48,0:55:45.49,Default,Kid Kenma,0,0,0,,You're the one who brought this.
Dialogue: 5,0:55:45.49,0:55:48.43,Default,Kid Kenma,0,0,0,,Bring the one from last week again next time.
Dialogue: 5,0:55:48.43,0:55:49.24,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 5,0:55:50.93,0:55:53.91,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,Kenma, you gotta be a setter!
Dialogue: 5,0:55:53.91,0:55:56.62,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,You'd be like the team mastermind. It'd be cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.62,0:55:59.21,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(359,1009)\fscx145\fscy145\fax-0.17\fnArial Rounded MT Bold\bord6\shad6\c&H225D8D&\3c&H225D8D&\4a&HC0&\blur1}Mastermind
Dialogue: 1,0:55:56.62,0:55:59.21,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(359,1009)\fscx145\fscy145\fax-0.17\fnArial Rounded MT Bold\c&H6BFCFC&\blur1}Mastermind
Dialogue: 5,0:55:57.64,0:55:59.21,Default,Kid Kenma,0,0,0,,The mastermind...
Dialogue: 5,0:55:59.21,0:56:04.09,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,The setter doesn't have to move as much, either.
Dialogue: 5,0:56:05.09,0:56:06.74,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,Well? Well?!
Dialogue: 5,0:56:06.74,0:56:08.14,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was a lie.
Dialogue: 5,0:56:10.81,0:56:13.46,Default,Friend A,0,0,0,,Hurry up or someone will get the field first!
Dialogue: 5,0:56:13.46,0:56:14.81,Default,Kenma's Father,0,0,0,,Hey, Tetsu!
Dialogue: 5,0:56:15.35,0:56:21.19,Default,Kenma's Father,0,0,0,,I was just wondering if you might bring Kenma with you to play soccer sometimes.
Dialogue: 5,0:56:23.66,0:56:26.59,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,I don't think he'd want to.
Dialogue: 5,0:56:26.59,0:56:29.66,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,I know how it feels to not want to.
Dialogue: 5,0:56:29.95,0:56:34.44,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,I'd bring him if he wanted to, but I don't think he does.
Dialogue: 5,0:56:34.44,0:56:38.88,Default,Kid Kuroo,0,0,0,,But he goes all-out for the stuff he likes, so don't worry!
Dialogue: 5,0:56:40.44,0:56:41.45,Default,Kenma's Father,0,0,0,,Yeah, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:56:46.68,0:56:50.26,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,If you were just some socialite jock,\N I wouldn't play with you.
Dialogue: 5,0:56:51.02,0:56:54.27,Default,Kuro,0,0,0,,Huh? What's with you attacking me all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 5,0:56:54.93,0:56:58.97,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,If I didn't have to, I wouldn't work up a sweat.
Dialogue: 5,0:56:58.97,0:57:02.00,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,I'd rather game than practice.
Dialogue: 5,0:57:02.00,0:57:05.29,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,And I probably like watching volleyball more than playing.
Dialogue: 5,0:57:05.99,0:57:06.49,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:57:11.93,0:57:16.91,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,In the end, I guess feeling obligated to play isn't all that bad.
Dialogue: 5,0:57:12.56,0:57:16.91,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,{\an8}All right!
Dialogue: 5,0:57:20.29,0:57:23.69,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,{\an8}Call me Straight-striker Tora!
Dialogue: 5,0:57:20.77,0:57:24.50,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,The whole team is a bunch of weirdos.
Dialogue: 5,0:57:23.69,0:57:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}More?
Dialogue: 5,0:57:24.50,0:57:25.59,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,{\an8}More!
Dialogue: 5,0:57:25.59,0:57:29.01,Default,Nekoma Cheering Squad,0,0,0,,{\an8}Go, go, Nekoma! Push it, push it, Nekoma!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.59,0:57:29.01,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1069,277)\fscx192\fscy192\fnDIST Inking Bold\fsp4.5\b1\c&H211C1F&\blur1.3}Connect
Dialogue: 5,0:57:29.91,0:57:32.22,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,The hard part is over.
Dialogue: 5,0:57:32.81,0:57:34.24,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,It's time to have fun!
Dialogue: 5,0:57:37.27,0:57:38.85,Default,Nekoma,0,0,0,,Woohoo!
Dialogue: 5,0:57:40.37,0:57:42.94,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Dunno what that's about, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:57:43.56,0:57:45.19,Default,Karasuno,0,0,0,,Woohoo!
Dialogue: 5,0:57:45.67,0:57:47.69,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,{\i1}And after our fun...
Dialogue: 5,0:57:48.27,0:57:50.20,Default,Sawamura,0,0,0,,{\i1}...one of our teams...
Dialogue: 5,0:57:51.20,0:57:52.56,Default,Kuroo and Sawamura,0,0,0,,{\i1}...will be out for good!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.29,0:58:03.50,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1005,103)\fscx132\fscy132\fnFrom Where You Are\c&HBAD0D3&\alpha&H50&\blur10}Karasuno High School Volleyball Team
Dialogue: 1,0:58:02.29,0:58:03.50,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1005,103)\fscx132\fscy132\fnFrom Where You Are\c&HBAD0D3&\blur1.3}Karasuno High School Volleyball Team
Dialogue: 5,0:58:08.42,0:58:10.13,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Left!
Dialogue: 5,0:58:12.66,0:58:14.39,Default,Tanaka and Karasuno,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:58:14.39,0:58:15.77,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Got somethin' to say?
Dialogue: 5,0:58:15.77,0:58:19.10,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,You lookin' for a fight, city boy?
Dialogue: 5,0:58:21.47,0:58:23.56,Default,Lev and Nekoma,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 5,0:58:24.24,0:58:26.40,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,I'm Nekoma's ace.
Dialogue: 5,0:58:26.40,0:58:27.41,Default,Sawamura,0,0,0,,Up front!
Dialogue: 5,0:58:28.11,0:58:29.45,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,Nice receive!
Dialogue: 5,0:58:29.45,0:58:30.07,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,High ball!
Dialogue: 5,0:58:32.63,0:58:33.53,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,Center!
Dialogue: 5,0:58:36.28,0:58:38.33,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,Ready, and...
Dialogue: 5,0:58:40.93,0:58:43.21,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,I'll jump even higher, to the very top!
Dialogue: 5,0:58:50.10,0:58:52.20,Default,Nekoma,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 5,0:58:52.20,0:58:54.11,Default,Keishin,0,0,0,,He was on that {\i1}fast{\i0}!
Dialogue: 5,0:58:54.11,0:58:56.99,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,Damn it, damn it, damn it, damn it, that was so cool!
Dialogue: 5,0:59:01.56,0:59:03.98,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,Number three, your receives were amazing!
Dialogue: 5,0:59:05.65,0:59:06.97,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,Nice receive!
Dialogue: 5,0:59:10.60,0:59:11.95,Default,Karasuno,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 5,0:59:13.11,0:59:15.93,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've been terrifying ever since that day...
Dialogue: 5,0:59:16.68,0:59:17.50,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yuu!
Dialogue: 5,0:59:25.21,0:59:27.17,Default,Kuro,0,0,0,,Can you block some balls for us?
Dialogue: 5,0:59:27.48,0:59:29.55,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,Oh, actually, I'm done for the night.
Dialogue: 5,0:59:30.13,0:59:32.57,Default,Bokuto,0,0,0,,Wanna come help us with spike practice again?
Dialogue: 5,0:59:32.57,0:59:34.88,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'll pass.
Dialogue: 5,0:59:37.47,0:59:39.70,Default,Kuro,0,0,0,,Blockers, try not to jump horizontally if you can!
Dialogue: 5,0:59:39.70,0:59:42.02,Default,Kuro,0,0,0,,If you can make it in time, come to a stop...
Dialogue: 5,0:59:43.39,0:59:44.36,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,...and then jump straight up.
Dialogue: 5,0:59:46.83,0:59:49.23,Default,Reserves,0,0,0,,Nice block! Let's score here!
Dialogue: 5,0:59:50.31,0:59:51.19,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,I touched it!
Dialogue: 5,0:59:51.19,0:59:53.90,Default,Nekoma Reserves,0,0,0,,Nice deflection! Let's score here!
Dialogue: 5,0:59:59.24,1:00:00.19,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 5,1:00:06.16,1:00:08.80,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,I'm genuinely curious about this.
Dialogue: 5,1:00:08.80,1:00:11.06,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,Why do you try so hard?
Dialogue: 5,1:00:12.98,1:00:15.95,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Tsukki, no need to play that hard.
Dialogue: 5,1:00:15.95,1:00:19.56,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,It's exhausting when the rally goes that long.
Dialogue: 5,1:00:20.68,1:00:22.87,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure this'd be over quicker...
Dialogue: 5,1:00:23.85,1:00:25.57,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,if {\i1}you{\i0} stopped trying so hard!
Dialogue: 5,1:00:26.60,1:00:30.40,Default,Kai,0,0,0,,I guess Tsukki's also the type to lose it when he gets tired.
Dialogue: 5,1:00:30.40,1:00:34.25,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,You and Bokuto take the blame for him, y'know!
Dialogue: 5,1:00:37.03,1:00:38.96,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,I oughta thank you.
Dialogue: 5,1:00:40.96,1:00:42.60,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Yeah, same.
Dialogue: 5,1:00:44.30,1:00:48.08,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Did you know watermelon seeds will sprout in your gut if you eat 'em?
Dialogue: 5,1:00:48.08,1:00:50.29,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Grow so big they burst—
Dialogue: 5,1:00:49.09,1:00:51.13,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah? I'll be careful, then.
Dialogue: 5,1:00:51.43,1:00:53.87,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Hey, did you know Bokuto's—
Dialogue: 5,1:00:53.87,1:00:56.13,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,Probably not, but that's fine.
Dialogue: 5,1:00:56.50,1:00:57.38,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Bokuto.
Dialogue: 5,1:00:57.38,1:00:58.62,Default,Bokuto,0,0,0,,Kuroo!
Dialogue: 5,1:00:59.34,1:01:01.26,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 5,1:01:04.35,1:01:08.33,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Focus your strength in your fingertips so\N that they won't be blown away by the ball.
Dialogue: 5,1:01:06.96,1:01:11.86,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,{\an8}When you're going against a spiker one-on-one, you generally don't stand in front of their body.
Dialogue: 5,1:01:11.86,1:01:14.12,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Center yourself on their dominant arm instead.
Dialogue: 5,1:01:11.86,1:01:13.47,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Listen up, kiddo!
Dialogue: 5,1:01:13.47,1:01:18.32,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Read blocking takes persistence and endurance, but it's also...
Dialogue: 5,1:01:18.32,1:01:20.57,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,the style of blocking where you get the last laugh.
Dialogue: 5,1:01:22.40,1:01:23.78,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.78,1:01:25.75,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(452,266)\fscx90\fscy90\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Nekoma
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.78,1:01:25.75,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1456,266)\fscx90\fscy90\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Karasuno
Dialogue: 5,1:01:25.75,1:01:27.12,Default,Azumane,0,0,0,,No worries!
Dialogue: 5,1:01:27.12,1:01:32.32,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,That impenetrable block of yours really ticks everyone off, yeah?
Dialogue: 5,1:01:33.21,1:01:37.22,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Well, I'm glad. Shows we did it right.
Dialogue: 5,1:01:34.46,1:01:37.22,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,{\an8}All right!
Dialogue: 5,1:01:37.52,1:01:39.38,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,If I say so myself.
Dialogue: 5,1:01:46.53,1:01:47.60,Default,Sawamura,0,0,0,,Get it!
Dialogue: 5,1:01:47.91,1:01:49.19,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Left!
Dialogue: 5,1:01:57.74,1:02:00.28,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit! I can't beat him!
Dialogue: 5,1:02:00.64,1:02:03.02,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,Center!
Dialogue: 5,1:02:04.53,1:02:06.95,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,{\i1}The net's the only place I stand a chance!
Dialogue: 5,1:02:07.34,1:02:09.16,Default,Yachi,0,0,0,,Here's your chance!
Dialogue: 5,1:02:10.76,1:02:12.12,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're terrifying.
Dialogue: 5,1:02:13.13,1:02:14.75,Default,Tsukishima,0,0,0,,{\i1}And because we're scared...
Dialogue: 5,1:02:15.63,1:02:17.76,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no time to think.
Dialogue: 5,1:02:18.07,1:02:21.37,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the end, it's going to be a quick battle of heights in the middle.
Dialogue: 5,1:02:22.96,1:02:24.77,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,{\i1}How're you enjoying this these days?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.56,1:02:37.44,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(452,266)\fscx90\fscy90\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Nekoma
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.56,1:02:37.44,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1456,266)\fscx90\fscy90\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Karasuno
Dialogue: 5,1:02:41.89,1:02:42.41,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Kenma!
Dialogue: 5,1:02:44.37,1:02:45.91,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Shouyou.
Dialogue: 5,1:02:45.91,1:02:51.14,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Remember when we met on the street the other day, \Nand you said you really didn't like volleyball that much?
Dialogue: 5,1:02:51.14,1:02:53.08,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Oh... yeah.
Dialogue: 5,1:02:53.73,1:02:55.58,Default,Karasuno,0,0,0,,Kageyama, give us another good serve!
Dialogue: 5,1:03:01.72,1:03:03.09,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,We can score here!
Dialogue: 5,1:03:10.81,1:03:12.06,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Get it!
Dialogue: 5,1:03:12.06,1:03:13.98,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,Nice save!
Dialogue: 5,1:03:22.21,1:03:23.96,Default,Nekoma,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 5,1:03:26.41,1:03:31.67,Default,Nekoma Cheering Squad,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nice, nice, Kozume! Nice, nice, Kozume! Do it again!
Dialogue: 5,1:03:31.67,1:03:33.93,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,There's something weird about you guys.
Dialogue: 5,1:03:34.65,1:03:37.62,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Like... you're rivals or something?
Dialogue: 5,1:03:37.62,1:03:40.34,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,What? We're just...
Dialogue: 5,1:03:43.31,1:03:44.66,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,friends.
Dialogue: 5,1:03:50.41,1:03:53.79,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,We'll swap Lev out when he's up to serve.
Dialogue: 5,1:03:52.82,1:03:54.73,Default,Inuoka; Lev,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,1:03:53.79,1:03:55.23,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,Up for it, Tamahiko?
Dialogue: 5,1:03:55.59,1:03:58.44,Default,Teshiro,0,0,0,,No, I don't think I'm ready.
Dialogue: 5,1:03:59.15,1:04:00.79,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,Maybe not.
Dialogue: 5,1:04:00.79,1:04:03.88,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,That honesty is what I like about you.
Dialogue: 5,1:04:03.13,1:04:04.46,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nice receive!
Dialogue: 5,1:04:03.88,1:04:08.89,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,The levelheadedness and courage it takes to say that is your strength.
Dialogue: 5,1:04:07.64,1:04:09.49,Default,Nekoma,0,0,0,,{\an8}All right!
Dialogue: 5,1:04:12.10,1:04:13.14,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,Get in there.
Dialogue: 5,1:04:13.14,1:04:14.91,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,Make it good, Tamahiko!
Dialogue: 5,1:04:15.19,1:04:19.17,Default,Teshiro,0,0,0,,{\i1}If they're putting a setter like me in as a pinch server,
Dialogue: 5,1:04:15.57,1:04:17.46,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tamahiko, we're counting on you!
Dialogue: 5,1:04:17.46,1:04:19.17,Default,Inuoka,0,0,0,,{\an8}You got this!
Dialogue: 5,1:04:19.17,1:04:22.32,Default,Teshiro,0,0,0,,{\i1}the plan must be to let Kozume play setter till the end.
Dialogue: 5,1:04:23.28,1:04:26.16,Default,Teshiro,0,0,0,,{\i1}Normally, he'd be out of gas by this point.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.85,1:04:32.22,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(452,266)\fscx90\fscy90\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Nekoma
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.85,1:04:32.22,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1456,266)\fscx90\fscy90\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Karasuno
Dialogue: 5,1:04:30.76,1:04:32.22,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Give us a good one!
Dialogue: 5,1:04:38.88,1:04:39.69,Default,Sawamura,0,0,0,,On it!
Dialogue: 5,1:04:39.69,1:04:40.52,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,All yours!
Dialogue: 5,1:04:40.52,1:04:41.19,Default,Sawamura,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 5,1:04:41.19,1:04:42.66,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,Azumane!
Dialogue: 5,1:04:42.66,1:04:44.10,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Ready, jump!
Dialogue: 5,1:04:45.69,1:04:46.65,Default,Saeko,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 5,1:04:48.36,1:04:49.18,Default,Mob A,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 5,1:04:49.18,1:04:50.07,Default,Mob B,0,0,0,,See that?
Dialogue: 5,1:04:52.24,1:04:54.30,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's headed over. Will they spike it? What now?
Dialogue: 5,1:04:54.30,1:04:56.97,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do I make them reach over? Take the rebound? Send it back?
Dialogue: 5,1:05:15.44,1:05:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,1:05:21.37,1:05:26.79,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Bring it!
Dialogue: 5,1:05:33.28,1:05:34.54,Default,Kuroo; Inuoka; Kageyama; Tsukishima,0,0,0,,{\i1}A tip?!
Dialogue: 5,1:05:37.16,1:05:38.37,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,{\i1}He knows!
Dialogue: 5,1:05:38.84,1:05:39.83,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's mine!
Dialogue: 5,1:06:03.88,1:06:04.69,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,1:06:06.91,1:06:09.86,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,How about today? How did you like winning?
Dialogue: 5,1:06:10.77,1:06:11.80,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Next time,
Dialogue: 5,1:06:12.69,1:06:14.33,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,I'll make you desperate to win,
Dialogue: 5,1:06:14.76,1:06:17.05,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,And then I'll make you say, \N"I hate losing!" or "That was a blast!"
Dialogue: 5,1:06:17.05,1:06:19.29,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,You'll start talking differently about the match!
Dialogue: 5,1:06:20.76,1:06:22.74,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Hey, Kenma! You okay?
Dialogue: 5,1:06:22.74,1:06:24.00,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Did you hurt something?
Dialogue: 5,1:06:30.05,1:06:32.97,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,This is fun.
Dialogue: 5,1:06:43.01,1:06:49.78,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,1:06:49.78,1:06:54.24,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.00,1:07:10.46,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(452,266)\fscx90\fscy90\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Nekoma
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.00,1:07:10.46,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1456,266)\fscx90\fscy90\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1}Karasuno
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.46,1:07:13.05,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1460,940)\fscx80\fscy87\fnLeviBrush\c&HD6D3D3&\alpha&HE0&\blur7.5}Fly
Dialogue: 1,1:07:10.46,1:07:13.05,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1460,940)\fscx80\fscy87\fnLeviBrush\c&HD6D3D3&\blur1}Fly
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.05,1:07:15.59,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(722,789)\fscx42\fscy42\frz4.1\fax-0.08\fnDIST Inking Bold\fsp4.5\b1\c&H19131F&\blur1.3}Connect
Dialogue: 5,1:07:20.60,1:07:24.52,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,When the hero's dying, I heal him and make him fight.
Dialogue: 5,1:07:24.52,1:07:29.64,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Sometimes he goes down and I revive him to fight.
Dialogue: 5,1:07:29.64,1:07:35.99,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,But from now on, I think I might at least feel sorry for forcing him to fight.
Dialogue: 5,1:07:35.99,1:07:38.48,Default,Yamamoto; Kuroo; Inuoka; Yaku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still to the brink of death?
Dialogue: 5,1:07:38.48,1:07:39.60,Default,Fukunaga,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 5,1:07:41.20,1:07:43.93,Default,Fukunaga,0,0,0,,People don't usually die in volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.92,1:07:49.88,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(535,239)\fscx190\fscy208\frz-41.03\fax1\fnLeviBrush\c&HD6D3D3&\alpha&HD0&\blur7.5}Fly
Dialogue: 1,1:07:45.92,1:07:49.88,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(535,239)\fscx190\fscy208\frz-41.03\fax1\fnLeviBrush\c&HD6D3D3&\blur1}Fly
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.92,1:07:49.88,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1384,180)\fscx113\fscy113\frz42.59\fax-1\fnDIST Inking Bold\fsp4.5\b1\c&H211B29&\blur1.3}Connect
Dialogue: 5,1:07:51.43,1:07:52.59,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,On it!
Dialogue: 5,1:07:53.61,1:07:55.93,Default,Sawamura; Tanaka; Hinata; Tsukishima; Azumane,0,0,0,,{\i1}Full-team synchronized attack!
Dialogue: 5,1:07:57.99,1:07:59.01,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,I touched it!
Dialogue: 5,1:07:59.83,1:08:01.34,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nice receive!
Dialogue: 5,1:07:59.83,1:08:04.60,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think I know exactly how Shouyou feels.
Dialogue: 5,1:08:05.30,1:08:09.54,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even on the brink of death,\N he pushes himself to beat the boss.
Dialogue: 5,1:08:09.54,1:08:12.12,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Always thinking contradicting thoughts.
Dialogue: 5,1:08:12.88,1:08:15.28,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Don't die on me!"
Dialogue: 5,1:08:15.62,1:08:16.74,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Left!
Dialogue: 5,1:08:20.70,1:08:22.91,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Kenma!
Dialogue: 5,1:08:24.00,1:08:24.62,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Not yet."
Dialogue: 5,1:08:26.02,1:08:26.43,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Not yet."
Dialogue: 5,1:08:26.43,1:08:28.33,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 5,1:08:31.70,1:08:32.83,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,Nice receive!
Dialogue: 5,1:08:34.87,1:08:36.43,Default,Karasuno Crowd,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 5,1:09:22.89,1:09:24.74,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Go get 'em, Kageyama!
Dialogue: 5,1:09:36.72,1:09:37.52,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,Taketora.
Dialogue: 5,1:09:37.52,1:09:38.33,Default,Yamamoto,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 5,1:09:42.20,1:09:43.38,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,Kenma?!
Dialogue: 5,1:09:43.38,1:09:45.18,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Idiot! The ball!
Dialogue: 5,1:09:45.18,1:09:46.68,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,It's still up!
Dialogue: 5,1:09:53.99,1:09:55.40,Default,Nishinoya,0,0,0,,Nice, Daichi!
Dialogue: 5,1:09:59.12,1:10:00.25,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm worn out...
Dialogue: 5,1:10:01.12,1:10:02.23,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exhausted...
Dialogue: 5,1:10:06.64,1:10:07.77,Default,Kai,0,0,0,,Finish it off!
Dialogue: 5,1:10:11.70,1:10:13.39,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I don't want it to end!
Dialogue: 5,1:10:14.04,1:10:15.38,Default,Sugawara,0,0,0,,We can score here!
Dialogue: 5,1:10:15.38,1:10:17.03,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Left!
Dialogue: 5,1:10:18.23,1:10:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 5,1:11:17.24,1:11:18.20,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Too much sweat...
Dialogue: 5,1:11:28.85,1:11:30.89,Default,Habuka,0,0,0,,That was from the sweat.
Dialogue: 5,1:11:31.20,1:11:33.39,Default,Habuka,0,0,0,,You could see the ball slip.
Dialogue: 5,1:11:33.39,1:11:35.40,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,That's what did it?
Dialogue: 5,1:11:35.77,1:11:40.84,Default,Habuka,0,0,0,,The sweat from everyone in that rally is on that ball.
Dialogue: 5,1:11:42.96,1:11:45.61,Default,Ogano,0,0,0,,That was awesome.
Dialogue: 5,1:11:48.46,1:11:50.48,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Tanaka, give us a good serve!
Dialogue: 5,1:11:50.48,1:11:51.67,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.04,1:11:55.25,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1022,525)\fscx58\fscy58\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H0C0C0C&\blur1.2}Nekoma
