Dialogue: 5,1:12:29.32,1:12:31.39,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whether we win,
Dialogue: 5,1:12:32.20,1:12:33.53,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}or whether we lose,
Dialogue: 5,1:12:34.46,1:12:36.36,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}no one dies.
Dialogue: 5,1:12:36.36,1:12:37.83,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}No one comes back to life.
Dialogue: 5,1:12:38.49,1:12:40.13,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Evil doesn't prevail.
Dialogue: 5,1:12:40.72,1:12:42.44,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}The world doesn't end.
Dialogue: 5,1:12:43.48,1:12:46.49,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}A vast world doesn't await.
