Dialogue: 5,1:12:47.05,1:12:54.76,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,{\i1}But here we are in a 9x18 meter rectangle, giving everything just to keep a ball in the air.
Dialogue: 5,1:12:57.01,1:13:01.02,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Man, that was fun.
Dialogue: 5,1:13:05.72,1:13:06.95,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Kuro.
Dialogue: 5,1:13:07.56,1:13:11.40,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Thanks for introducing me to volleyball.
Dialogue: 5,1:13:19.86,1:13:21.74,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Uh, sure...
Dialogue: 5,1:13:24.42,1:13:25.24,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,1:13:28.60,1:13:30.76,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait! Hang on now, you moron!
Dialogue: 5,1:13:30.76,1:13:32.97,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,What? Why are you mad?
Dialogue: 5,1:13:42.16,1:13:43.29,Default,Ref,0,0,0,,Line up!
Dialogue: 5,1:13:43.29,1:13:47.15,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Ugh. I guarantee I'll have a fever after this.
Dialogue: 5,1:13:48.45,1:13:50.60,Default,Teshiro,0,0,0,,I wanna be on that court.
Dialogue: 5,1:13:50.60,1:13:52.10,Default,Lev,0,0,0,,You were.
Dialogue: 5,1:13:52.10,1:13:53.83,Default,Teshiro,0,0,0,,Really be on it.
Dialogue: 5,1:13:55.27,1:13:57.86,Default,Teshiro,0,0,0,,I wanna play volleyball like that.
Dialogue: 5,1:14:00.36,1:14:02.60,Default,Both teams,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 5,1:14:09.28,1:14:12.22,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,Never knew you could get through blocks like that.
Dialogue: 5,1:14:12.69,1:14:13.86,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,No, yeah!
Dialogue: 5,1:14:13.86,1:14:15.43,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,Which is it?
Dialogue: 5,1:14:30.92,1:14:34.46,Default,Tendo,0,0,0,,Bet you'd hit 'em like home runs outta the court if we played the kitty cats.
Dialogue: 5,1:14:34.46,1:14:35.99,Default,Goshiki,0,0,0,,Wh-What?! No, I wouldn't!
Dialogue: 5,1:14:35.99,1:14:40.46,Default,Tendo,0,0,0,,Never knew the little demon crow could attack a high set, though.
Dialogue: 5,1:14:40.46,1:14:41.96,Default,Goshiki,0,0,0,,I won't be beat!
Dialogue: 5,1:14:54.09,1:14:55.77,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Thanks, Tsukki.
Dialogue: 5,1:14:55.77,1:14:57.10,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,You were awesome!
Dialogue: 5,1:15:28.76,1:15:30.26,Default,Karasuno,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 5,1:15:31.28,1:15:33.45,Default,Nekoma,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.01,1:15:40.06,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(266,440)\fscx47\fscy47\frz21.49\fax-0.08\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\b1\c&H121212&\alpha&HD0&\blur7.5}Tokyo\N{\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\fs100\c&HC99852&}Nekoma
Dialogue: 1,1:15:36.01,1:15:40.06,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(266,440)\fscx47\fscy47\frz21.49\fax-0.08\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\b1\c&H121212&\blur1.2}Tokyo\N{\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\fs100\c&HC99852&}Nekoma
Dialogue: 5,1:15:40.90,1:15:45.02,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,We'll save the nitpicking for later.
Dialogue: 5,1:15:46.17,1:15:49.23,Default,Nekomata,0,0,0,,You boys played well. Thank you.
Dialogue: 5,1:15:55.52,1:15:57.16,Default,Kuroo and Kenma,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 5,1:15:57.84,1:16:00.16,Default,Nekoma,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 5,1:16:09.59,1:16:14.54,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,Man, it's over already? Sure doesn't feel like it.
Dialogue: 5,1:16:14.54,1:16:15.93,Default,Kai,0,0,0,,It's all over,
Dialogue: 5,1:16:16.28,1:16:20.18,Default,Kai,0,0,0,,but I'm glad I was with you guys these past three years.
Dialogue: 5,1:16:23.44,1:16:26.22,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,Don't you gimme that, Kai! Seriously, stop!
Dialogue: 5,1:16:26.22,1:16:28.52,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Jeez! What's with all of you?!
Dialogue: 5,1:16:33.79,1:16:35.30,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,Could you at least crouch?
Dialogue: 5,1:16:35.30,1:16:37.16,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,I'm floating over here!
Dialogue: 5,1:16:37.16,1:16:40.59,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,People are gonna think I busted my leg again!
Dialogue: 5,1:16:40.59,1:16:41.71,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Kenma!
Dialogue: 5,1:16:45.53,1:16:46.29,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,I look—
Dialogue: 5,1:16:45.53,1:16:46.83,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,{\an8}I look forward to playing again.
Dialogue: 5,1:16:47.92,1:16:50.62,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Hey! That was my line!
Dialogue: 5,1:16:50.62,1:16:52.80,Default,Kageyama,0,0,0,,What? Who cares?
Dialogue: 5,1:16:53.57,1:16:54.37,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Kenma.
Dialogue: 5,1:16:55.06,1:16:56.80,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Let's play again next year!
Dialogue: 5,1:17:00.32,1:17:02.25,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's.
Dialogue: 5,1:17:07.88,1:17:10.12,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Kenma! We're leaving!
Dialogue: 5,1:17:10.12,1:17:11.65,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 5,1:17:12.17,1:17:14.65,Default,Kenma,0,0,0,,See you around, Shouyou.
Dialogue: 5,1:17:14.65,1:17:16.71,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,Yeah, catch ya around!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.94,1:17:52.89,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}We won't say goodbye
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.89,1:17:55.30,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}Don't need a promise
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.30,1:17:59.78,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}Because we will see each other again
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.78,1:18:04.96,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}A horizon like a bite out of an orange
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.96,1:18:09.69,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}A bittersweet light so dazzling
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.69,1:18:14.51,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}Sweat pouring out and voices bellowing
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.51,1:18:19.08,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}Shoulders bumping as we laugh and cry
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.08,1:18:25.11,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}As we head for tomorrow and an orange sky
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.11,1:18:28.58,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}Our wings are spread wide
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.58,1:18:33.46,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}One more second, just one more second
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.46,1:18:38.24,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}For us to savor our most irreplaceable moment
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.24,1:18:40.62,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}I'm sure
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.46,1:18:49.36,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}Our backs were small
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.36,1:18:56.12,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}Yet they carried our big dreams all this way
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.12,1:19:01.38,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}The future we've reached didn't go exactly as hoped
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.38,1:19:06.18,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}But it was a hell of a time all the same
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.18,1:19:10.91,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}We ran out of breath but we kept running
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.91,1:19:15.42,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}What we were chasing was the fire in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.42,1:19:24.94,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}We've all been tied to this one moment, never to be repeated
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.94,1:19:29.86,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}What did we envision? What did we hope to accomplish?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.86,1:19:34.66,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}All you can do is try to imagine
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.66,1:19:38.18,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}I'm sure
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.26,1:19:47.79,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}So sure
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.93,1:19:59.78,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}I'm positive you'll come to understand it one day
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.78,1:20:04.66,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}So don't be afraid to make mistakes
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.66,1:20:07.42,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}You're fine being you
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.59,1:20:20.12,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}Like a slightly bitter orange the aftertaste lingers
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.12,1:20:25.08,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}One more second, just one more second
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.08,1:20:29.86,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}Don't be torn by regret as you go
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.86,1:20:39.36,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}You might unexpectedly start yearning again for these treasured times
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.36,1:20:44.26,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}Don't stop in place, don't look back
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.26,1:20:49.07,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}Keep on forging your path and you'll be fine
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.07,1:20:51.84,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}I'm sure
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.64,1:21:02.05,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}So sure
Dialogue: 5,1:21:14.84,1:21:17.20,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Looks like the match on Court A won't be long.
Dialogue: 5,1:21:17.20,1:21:20.56,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's tourney favorite Itachiyama for ya.
Dialogue: 5,1:21:23.19,1:21:26.84,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,Wow! He's even taller up close!
Dialogue: 5,1:21:26.84,1:21:29.84,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,He's faking most of his height with that hair.
Dialogue: 5,1:21:29.84,1:21:31.41,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,I'm not deaf, you know.
Dialogue: 5,1:21:31.96,1:21:34.16,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,Sorry, babe. Can I have a sec?
Dialogue: 5,1:21:34.16,1:21:35.18,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 5,1:21:35.18,1:21:37.08,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,I'm gonna check out the shop.
Dialogue: 5,1:21:37.08,1:21:38.87,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.38,1:21:48.80,signs,,0,0,0,,{\move(175,111,138,69,20,4420)\frz18.62\fax0.1\fnBloodyslime\fs80\c&HBEA89B&\alpha&HD0&\blur7.5\fad(186,0)\t(\fscx105\fscy105)}Losers
Dialogue: 1,1:21:44.38,1:21:48.80,signs,,0,0,0,,{\move(175,111,138,69,20,4420)\frz18.62\fax0.1\fnBloodyslime\fs80\c&HBEA89B&\blur1.3\fad(186,0)\t(\fscx105\fscy105)}Losers
Dialogue: 5,1:21:44.64,1:21:48.80,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,Welcome to the other side!
Dialogue: 5,1:21:51.05,1:21:53.29,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Someone snap a pic of that face!
Dialogue: 5,1:21:53.29,1:21:54.78,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,We're gonna show it to Mika!
Dialogue: 5,1:21:54.78,1:21:57.48,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,Listen. Don't let it get to you.
Dialogue: 5,1:21:57.48,1:22:01.59,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,Every team here save one is gonna wind up losing.
Dialogue: 5,1:22:01.59,1:22:04.94,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,Only difference is when. It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 5,1:22:05.45,1:22:09.15,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you really thought you could win the whole thing.
Dialogue: 5,1:22:11.94,1:22:18.47,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Sure, most of us don't absolutely 100% believe we'll win.
Dialogue: 5,1:22:18.47,1:22:20.99,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,C'mon. You're not even gonna get mad?
Dialogue: 5,1:22:20.99,1:22:22.63,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,Where's the fun in that?
Dialogue: 5,1:22:25.22,1:22:29.65,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,It doesn't really even matter whether we can win or not.
Dialogue: 5,1:22:30.30,1:22:34.80,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,We don't stop because we can't win, nor do we play because we can win.
Dialogue: 5,1:22:35.21,1:22:36.82,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,I'm well aware, dumbass!
Dialogue: 5,1:22:36.82,1:22:39.62,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,Watch the language now, Daishou. I'm gonna start recording.
Dialogue: 5,1:22:39.62,1:22:42.73,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,Rich of you to get mad over a fight you started!
Dialogue: 5,1:22:43.01,1:22:45.51,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,Screw off and shut your face!
Dialogue: 5,1:22:45.51,1:22:46.49,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,All set?
Dialogue: 5,1:22:47.44,1:22:48.73,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,1:22:48.73,1:22:50.34,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,How long were you there?
Dialogue: 5,1:22:50.34,1:22:52.24,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,What should we have for lunch?
Dialogue: 5,1:22:52.24,1:22:54.18,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,Maybe omelets?
Dialogue: 5,1:22:54.18,1:22:55.18,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,Nice choice!
Dialogue: 5,1:22:55.18,1:22:56.54,Default,Yaku,0,0,0,,What's his deal?
Dialogue: 5,1:22:56.54,1:22:58.05,Default,Kuroo,0,0,0,,He's a riot.
Dialogue: 5,1:22:59.60,1:23:02.75,Default,Daisho,0,0,0,,Bet there's lots of great food around here.
Dialogue: 5,1:23:10.88,1:23:15.97,Default,Kai,0,0,0,,Most of us don't absolutely 100% believe we'll win.
Dialogue: 5,1:23:17.22,1:23:19.33,Default,Kai,0,0,0,,And maybe it's not about "believing" for them,
Dialogue: 5,1:23:20.43,1:23:23.93,Default,Kai,0,0,0,,but there are definitely guys who are focused on winning.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.50,1:23:46.46,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(432,403)\fscx66\fscy66\fax0.19\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H121212&\blur1}K{\fax0.182}a{\fax0.175}m{\fax0.168}o{\fax0.16}m{\fax0.152}e{\fax0.145}d{\fax0.138}a{\fax0.13}i
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.50,1:23:46.46,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1500,401)\fscx66\fscy66\fax-0.14\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\c&H121212&\blur1}T{\fax-0.147}a{\fax-0.153}k{\fax-0.16}a{\fax-0.167}g{\fax-0.173}i{\fax-0.18}y{\fax-0.187}a{\fax-0.193}m{\fax-0.2}a
Dialogue: 5,1:23:47.34,1:23:51.63,Default,Yachi,0,0,0,,{\i1}They'll be up against Kamomedai High School in the quarterfinals.
Dialogue: 5,1:23:48.48,1:23:50.02,Default,Kamomedai and Takagiyama,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 5,1:23:51.63,1:23:53.93,Default,Yachi,0,0,0,,{\i1}The quarterfinals...
Dialogue: 5,1:23:54.93,1:23:57.28,Default,Hoshiumi,0,0,0,,Are you paying attention to me because I'm small?
Dialogue: 5,1:23:58.24,1:24:02.70,Default,Hoshiumi,0,0,0,,Even though being smaller puts you at a disadvantage in volleyball,
Dialogue: 5,1:24:02.70,1:24:05.05,Default,Hoshiumi,0,0,0,,it doesn't make you completely helpless!
Dialogue: 5,1:24:07.80,1:24:10.26,Default,Hoshiumi,0,0,0,,I caught your second and third matches.
Dialogue: 5,1:24:10.26,1:24:11.94,Default,Hoshiumi,0,0,0,,Nice work.
Dialogue: 5,1:24:13.92,1:24:17.16,Default,Hoshiumi,0,0,0,,It's about time we see who's the real...
Dialogue: 5,1:24:20.24,1:24:21.53,Default,Hoshiumi,0,0,0,,Little Giant!

